NK121(ko)004:1: // zur chung shes rab grags pa'i zhal gyi gdams pa
NK121(ko)004:2: brgyad cu pa bslab gsum rin po che'i gdams ngag
NK121(ko)004:3: gi mchan 'grel rin po che'i phreng ba bzhugs so
NK121(ko)004:4: // sde snod spyi dang mdo sgyu sems gsum gyi snying po'i man ngag go //
NK121(ko)004:5: na mo rat+na gu ru b+h+yah rdo rje sems dngos bla ma la //
NK121(ko)004:6: btud nas bslab gsum rin chen mdzod //
NK121(ko)004:7: zhal gdams brgyad cu'i sa bcad dang //
NK121(ko)004:8: gzhung chen rin chen phreng ba spel //
NK121(ko)004:9: de la sangs rgyas kyis sems can gyi blo rigs
NK121(ko)004:10: sna tshogs la dgongs te chos theg pa sna tshogs
NK121(ko)004:11: gsungs pa las / bde gshegs rgyal po bas mdo rgyud bal bzhin g.yengs /
NK121(ko)004:13: mkhas pa rnams kyi rgya gad chu bzhin 'thungs /
NK121(ko)004:14: gong ma rnams kyi dgongs nyams lan tsh+wa bzhin du myong /
NK121(ko)004:15: snang tshul 'di la me long bzhin bltas pas /
NK121(ko)004:16: gang ltar byas kyang duhkha 'ba' zhig las mi 'dug pas /
NK121(ko)004:17: 'jig rten blos gtong dgos par mthong /
NK121(ko)004:18: phyi ma'i don gcig ma 'grub na mi phan pas /
NK121(ko)004:19: che grags mchil snabs bzhin dor dgos par mthong /
NK121(ko)004:20: mi'i ngo srung dka' bas 'khor dang 'du 'dzi spangs
NK121(ko)004:21: la gcig pur bsgom dgos par mthong bas brag rgya
NK121(ko)004:22: bor sgrub pa drag po mdzad do //
NK121(ko)004:23: des chos thams cad kyi lag len zhal gdams brgyad cu rang gis nyams su myong ba /
NK121(ko)004:24: skye shi'i 'jigs pa rnams kyi nyi ma de ring gi lag len /
NK121(ko)004:25: byams pas snying gtam rang gi sha la bab pa'i
NK121(ko)004:26: gros 'debs dang 'dra ba 'di rdol chos su gsungs
NK121(ko)004:29: dad pa'i kun slong brtan byas nas //
NK121(ko)004:30: tshul khrims dag pa'i zhing sa la //
NK121(ko)004:31: ting nge 'dzin gyi sa bon gdab //
NK121(ko)004:32: shes rab lo tog smin par byed //
NK121(ko)004:34: 'jug sgo dad pa la gdams pa /
NK121(ko)004:35: gzhi tshul khrims la gdams pa /
NK121(ko)004:36: thabs ting nge 'dzin la gdams pa /
NK121(ko)004:37: ngo bo shes rab la gdams pa /
NK121(ko)004:38: de rnams kyi mjug bsdu ba'o //
NK121(ko)004:39: dang po la le'u lnga las /
NK121(ko)004:40: le'u dang po dad pa sngon du 'gro dgos pa dang /
NK121(ko)004:41: dad pa med pa'i skyon bstan pa ni //
NK121(ko)004:42: chos thams cad kyi sngon du 'gro bas /
NK121(ko)004:43: dad pa med pa'i skyon dang /
NK121(ko)004:44: yod pa'i yon tan shes par bya ba gal che /
NK121(ko)004:45: de yang dad pa'i ngo bo ni /
NK121(ko)004:46: rang rgyud dang rnam dkar gyi chos dbyer mi phyed pa /
NK121(ko)004:48: gang don du gnyer ba de'i 'dod pa /
NK121(ko)004:49: dbye na dngas 'dod yid ches kyi dad pa gsum mo //
NK121(ko)004:50: de la dad pa med pa'i skyon drug ni /
NK121(ko)004:51: dad pa med pa rgya mtsho'i gting gi pha wong dang 'dra /
NK121(ko)004:52: chos kyis rang rgyud la mi phan /
NK121(ko)004:53: mnyan pa med pa'i gru dang 'dra /
NK121(ko)004:54: 'khor ba'i pha rol du mi bgrod /
NK121(ko)004:55: long ba lha khang du phyin pa dang 'dra //
NK121(ko)004:56: byang chub kyi myu gu mi 'byung /
NK121(ko)004:57: g.yang mo 'khor dong du tshud pa dang 'dra /
NK121(ko)004:58: sdug bsngal gyi gnas nas mi thar /
NK121(ko)004:59: lag rdum gser gling du phyin pa dang 'dra'o bu /
NK121(ko)004:60: dal 'byor stong log tu 'gro ba'i skyon yod do ///
NK121(ko)004:61: le'u gnyis pa dad pa'i yon tan ni //
NK121(ko)004:62: dad pa'i yon tan drug la /
NK121(ko)004:63: dad pa zhing sa gshin po dang 'dra /
NK121(ko)004:64: dkar po'i lo tog thams cad 'phel /
NK121(ko)004:65: dad pa yid bzhin nor bu dang 'dra /
NK121(ko)004:66: rang gzhan gyi dgos 'dod thams cad 'byung /
NK121(ko)004:67: dad pa khrims chags pa'i rgyal po dang 'dra /
NK121(ko)004:69: dad pa gags yod pa'i mkhar zin pa dang /
NK121(ko)004:70: nyes pas mi gos shing yon tan thams cad sdud /
NK121(ko)004:71: dad pa chu bo chen po'i gzings dang 'dra /
NK121(ko)004:72: skye rga na 'chi'i sdug bsngal las grol /
NK121(ko)004:73: dad pa 'jigs sar skyel ma dang 'dra'o bu /
NK121(ko)004:74: 'khor ba dang ngan song gi 'jigs pa las sgrol bar byed pa'o //
NK121(ko)004:76: dad pa'i yon tan blang bya de nyid nyer len rgyu'i tshul du gsos gdab pa ni //
NK121(ko)004:77: dad pa skye ba'i rgyu rkyen bcu la /
NK121(ko)004:78: da ltar byed spyod grogs dang bcas pa 'di la bde ba med par shes dgos /
NK121(ko)004:79: nam phugs sdug bsngal gyi rgyu yin /
NK121(ko)004:80: las rgyu 'bras la yid ches dgos /
NK121(ko)004:81: nam yang bslu ba mi srid /
NK121(ko)004:82: 'chi ba mi rtag pa rjes su dran dgos /
NK121(ko)004:84: 'khor 'dab longs spyod rnams dang mi 'grogs par 'gro ba dran dgos /
NK121(ko)004:85: rang 'chi dus thams cad skyur nas 'gro bas phan med /
NK121(ko)004:86: phyi ma'i skye gnas la 'dam dbang med pa dran dgos /
NK121(ko)004:87: las dbang gis gar 'gro nges pa med /
NK121(ko)004:88: mi lus gtsang ma 'di lta bu thob par dka' ba dran dgos /
NK121(ko)004:89: dal 'byor gyi ngo bo dang rgyu rkyen tshogs pa dka'/
NK121(ko)004:90: 'khor ba thams cad duhkha 'dug pa dran dgos /
NK121(ko)004:91: nam yang sdug bsngal gsum las ma 'das /
NK121(ko)004:92: dkon mchog gsum gyi che ba'i yon tan mthong dgos /
NK121(ko)004:93: gtan du 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal las skyob nges /
NK121(ko)004:94: dam pa rnams kyi mdzad spyod mthong dgos /
NK121(ko)004:95: sku gsung thugs kyi mdzad pa la nyes skyon gyi dri ma med /
NK121(ko)004:96: grogs bzang po dge ba la gnas pa dang 'grogs dgos bu /
NK121(ko)004:97: des rang nyid la bzang spyod shugs kyis 'gos pas
NK121(ko)004:98: dad sogs dkar chos rnams gong 'phel du 'gyur ro
NK121(ko)004:100: zhen log gi chos bcu gsum gyis rang gis rang la shag gdab pa ni //
NK121(ko)004:102: pha yul rgyab tu ma bskyur na nga rgyal gyi bdud mi chom /
NK121(ko)004:104: khyim gyi bya ba ma btang na chos bya ba'i skabs mi rnyed /
NK121(ko)004:106: dad pa nam skyes su ma thon na bya ba'i las la zin pa mi 'ong /
NK121(ko)004:108: rang la dad pa med pa'i bsnyad kha gzhan la ma bsgo /
NK121(ko)004:110: rang gi yo byad rlung la ma bskur bas mi chos kyi kho thag mi chod /
NK121(ko)004:111: ci yod bla ma dang dkon mchog gi phyogs su phul /
NK121(ko)004:112: nye 'brel dang ma sring na chags sdang gi rgyun mi chad /
NK121(ko)004:114: dus da res ma byas na phyi ma gar 'gro cha med /
NK121(ko)004:115: mthun rkyen 'dzom dus 'dir 'khor ba las ci thar bya /
NK121(ko)004:116: da lta byar yod pa mi byed par phyi ma la smon lam 'debs pa kha skad yin /
NK121(ko)004:117: rang la nus pa yod bzhin mi byed la rang bslus /
NK121(ko)004:118: rang la brdzun mi zer na dam pa'i chos kyis /
NK121(ko)004:120: nam yang 'bor ba la da lta bor na don can 'gro /
NK121(ko)004:121: lus dang longs spyod ci yod chos phyogs su thongs /
NK121(ko)004:122: mi 'khyongs nges pa'i srid par yong ma bskyangs par 'khyong nges pa'i nyams myong skyongs /
NK121(ko)004:123: chos phyir dka' thub bzod thub par gyis /
NK121(ko)004:124: yong mi yong cha med pa'i sang phod kyi tshis ma byed nges pa'i /
NK121(ko)004:125: long med kyi blo sna bstung dgos /
NK121(ko)004:126: nyams su len pa la lto rgyab zhar la 'byung gis re dogs ma che bu /
NK121(ko)004:127: chos byed pa la tshe 'di blos thong ba gal che'o //
NK121(ko)004:129: gal che ba bcu gsum gyi sgo nas lam phyin ci ma log par bstan pa ni /
NK121(ko)004:130: 7 gal che ba bcu gsum la /
NK121(ko)004:131: rtogs pa nam mkha' ltar phyogs ris med pa /
NK121(ko)004:132: nyams myong rgya mtsho ltar bri gang med pa /
NK121(ko)004:133: thugs rje nyi ma ltar gsal 'grib med pa'i /
NK121(ko)004:134: yon tan gsum dang ldan pa'i bla ma la gus par bya ba gal che /
NK121(ko)004:135: lam gyi rtsa ba yin pas mnyes pa gsum gyi sgo nas bsten /
NK121(ko)004:136: ma gus pa'i las rmi lam du'ang mi bya /
NK121(ko)004:137: snod dang ldan pa'i slob ma la gdams ngag sbyin pa gal che /
NK121(ko)004:138: des brgyud pa 'dzin cing rang gzhan bstan 'gro'i don 'byung /
NK121(ko)004:139: chos la dpe mkhyud mi bya /
NK121(ko)004:140: phyi nang gi dngos po la chags zhen bskyur ba gal che /
NK121(ko)004:141: 'dod yon lnga la chags pa'i nyes dmigs dran par bya /
NK121(ko)004:142: gdams pa spyod pa'i phyir yun bsring ba gal che /
NK121(ko)004:143: chos la ngang thung mi bya /
NK121(ko)004:144: bla ma dang 'grogs yun ring dgos /
NK121(ko)004:146: lha dkon mchog la mos gus bskyed pa gal che /
NK121(ko)004:147: mos gus med na byin rlabs mi 'jug /
NK121(ko)004:149: dge ba'i chos la brtson 'grus bskyed pa gal che /
NK121(ko)004:150: dpe sgeg mo'i mgo la me shor ba ltar bya /
NK121(ko)004:151: le lo'i dbang du mi gtong /
NK121(ko)004:152: sdig pa mi dge ba'i chos la 'dzem pa gal che /
NK121(ko)004:153: rnam smin gyi 'bras bu bsam ste mig tu rdul spang ba ltar bya /
NK121(ko)004:154: rnam par mi rtog pa rgyud la bsten pa gal che /
NK121(ko)004:155: dug lnga'i rnam rtog rang sar zhi bar bya /
NK121(ko)004:156: rjes la snying rje byang chub kyi sems bsten pa gal che /
NK121(ko)004:157: theg chen lam gyi rtsa ba ya na pas nam yang med du mi rung /
NK121(ko)004:158: bdag bas gzhan gces pa la bslab /
NK121(ko)004:159: phyin ci ma log pa'i gdams ngag la nges shes skyes pa gal che /
NK121(ko)004:160: the tshom med na dngos grub myur du 'byung /
NK121(ko)004:161: sdom dang dam tshig la gnas pa gal che /
NK121(ko)004:162: rang rgyud sdom gsum gyi nyes ltung gis ma gos par bya /
NK121(ko)004:163: sems skye med du gtan la dbab pa gal che /
NK121(ko)004:164: snang sems chos nyid kyi rol pas sems nyid skye med nam mkha' ltar thag bcad /
NK121(ko)004:165: gsang ba'i man ngag snod ngan la mi ster ba gal che'o bu /
NK121(ko)004:166: des gsang ba 'khyal zhing sgro skur gyi rgyur 'gyur
NK121(ko)004:167: bas gzab ste gdul bya'i snod brtag pa gces so
NK121(ko)004:168: // zhal gyi gdams pa brgyad cu pa las /
NK121(ko)004:169: 'jug sgo dad pa brtan po la gdams pa'i skabs te dang po'o //
NK121(ko)004:170: rtsa ba'i sa bcad gnyis pa /
NK121(ko)004:171: rten rnam par dag pa lhag pa tshul khrims kyi bslab pa rin po che la gdams pa la /
NK121(ko)004:173: chos bya ba'i dus la babs par gdams pa ni /
NK121(ko)004:175: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa gnas pa dang dad pa
NK121(ko)004:176: dus 'dzom na tshe snga ma la bsod nams bsags
NK121(ko)004:177: pa yin / da res lan gcig rnyed pa'i dal 'byor 'di stong zad du ma gtong /
NK121(ko)004:178: rang chos la mos pa dang slob dpon gdams ngag
NK121(ko)004:179: can dang 'phrad na long bas rin po che rnyed
NK121(ko)004:180: pa yin / phyis yang yang rnyed dka' bas dpral ba'i mig ltar 'bral med yun du brten /
NK121(ko)004:181: skyon med pa'i lus la dad brtson shes rab 'dzom pa yon tan sbyang ba'i las 'phro yin /
NK121(ko)004:182: de gsum gong 'phel gyi thabs la brtson /
NK121(ko)004:183: rang 'khor bar skyes pa dang gnyen 'brel rgya gad
NK121(ko)004:184: zer ba 'dzom na chos la bskul ma 'debs pa
NK121(ko)004:185: yin / blo thag rang gis chod la chos kyis /
NK121(ko)004:186: rang la yo byad yod pa dang gtong la dga'
NK121(ko)004:187: ba dang slong mo pa dus 'dzom na sbyin pa
NK121(ko)004:188: rdzogs pa yin / ser sna'i mdud pas ma 'ching phyogs med du thongs /
NK121(ko)004:189: rang nyams su len pa'i dus su duhkha'i mtsho rdol na sdig pa 'dag pa yin /
NK121(ko)004:192: chos byed la ma nyes pa'i dgra byung na bzod pa'i lam la 'god pa yin /
NK121(ko)004:193: 'khon 'dzin spong la bzod pa'i phan yon dran par bya /
NK121(ko)004:194: rang la dad pa phul du byung ba dang gdams
NK121(ko)004:195: pa btab pa dus mnyam na las kyi mtha' rdzogs
NK121(ko)004:196: pa yin / phyis 'khor bar mi skye /
NK121(ko)004:197: chos thams cad chags sdang gi gnyen por 'gro bar bya /
NK121(ko)004:198: rang shi bas 'jigs pa dang gzhan shi ba dus
NK121(ko)004:199: 'dzoms na 'khor ba las blo ldog pa'i dus yin
NK121(ko)004:200: / tshe 'di'i bde skyid la ma chags par mdzod /
NK121(ko)004:201: sngon la tshe 'di'i bya ba bsgrubs la de nas
NK121(ko)004:202: chos gcig bya mno na bdud kyi bshol theb pa
NK121(ko)004:203: yin no bu / bdud dbang du ma song ba gal che'o //
NK121(ko)004:205: gdams pa bcu gsum gyi gdams ngag lag len gdams pa ni /
NK121(ko)004:207: bsgrub pa'i brtson 'grus kyi lcag tu bdag gzhan gyi 'chi ba la brtag /
NK121(ko)004:208: nam mchi nges pa med pas tshe 'di yi bya bzhag thams cad bor thongs /
NK121(ko)004:209: gus pa khyad par can skye bar 'dod pas bla ma'i phyi nang gi yon tan la brtag /
NK121(ko)004:211: skyon du snang ba de rang snang ma dag pas lan /
NK121(ko)004:212: spyod pa kun dang mthun par 'dod pas gzhan gyi rtsol ba mi dgag /
NK121(ko)004:213: theg pa thams cad rang sa bden pas chos dang grub matha'i kha 'dzin che /
NK121(ko)004:214: bla ma'i thugs zin pa mi 'gyur bar bya ba'i phyir nyams su len pa drag tu bya /
NK121(ko)004:215: yon tan ma lus pa rang la 'ong /
NK121(ko)004:216: dngos grub myur du thob par 'dod na sdom pa dam tshig ma nyams par bsrung /
NK121(ko)004:217: bsrung mtshams mtha' dag mi dge bcu dang dug lnga rang mtshan la slong bar 'du /
NK121(ko)004:218: chu bo bzhin bcad par 'dod pas kun gzhi skye med du rtsad bcad /
NK121(ko)004:219: kun gzhi skye med du shes par skye shi'i kha mi brgyud do //
NK121(ko)004:220: byang chub sgrub pa la bar chad med par 'dod pas tshe 'di'i g.yeng ba rgyab tu bor /
NK121(ko)004:221: mi nus pa'i gzhan don byed pa'ang g.yeng ba yin /
NK121(ko)004:222: rang ma smin par gzhan don ma byed /
NK121(ko)004:223: gzhan don 'bad med du 'grub par 'dod pas tshad med bzhi bsgom /
NK121(ko)004:224: byang chub kyi sems 'byong na ci byed gzhan don las mi 'da'/
NK121(ko)004:225: phyi ma ngan song gsum la 'tsher na mi dge ba bcu la 'dzem /
NK121(ko)004:226: rtag tu bag yod par bya /
NK121(ko)004:227: 'di dang phyi mar bde ba 'dod na dge ba bcu la 'bad /
NK121(ko)004:228: da lta 'dem kha yod dus blang dor go ma 'dzol /
NK121(ko)004:229: chos la blo 'jug par 'dod pas sdug bsngal gyi dka' ba nyams su blangs /
NK121(ko)004:230: ngal ba don med la bsam nas snying la rus pa bskyed /
NK121(ko)004:231: skyid de ba'i chos de sus kyang ma byung ba zhig yin /
NK121(ko)004:232: 'khor ba la blo ldog par 'dod pas bla na med pa'i byang chub btsal /
NK121(ko)004:233: thar ba byang chub kyi phan yon shes dgos /
NK121(ko)004:234: 'di theg pa gsum char la gal tshe /
NK121(ko)004:235: 'bras bu sku gsum thob par 'dod pas tshogs gnyis zung du 'jug go bu /
NK121(ko)004:236: des sku gsum la bsgribs pa'i dri ma sel ba'i rgyu byed do //
NK121(ko)004:238: dgos med lngas chos min ngos bzung ba ston pa ni /
NK121(ko)004:240: 'khor ba la blo ma log pa'i chos la mos pa skad byas pa la dgos pa med /
NK121(ko)004:241: ci byed tshe 'dir song nas chos mi 'grub /
NK121(ko)004:242: chos rnal ma byed pa la 'khor ba'i snang zhen ldog dgos /
NK121(ko)004:243: dngos po la snang zhen pa ma log pa'i stong nyid bsgoms pa la dgos pa med /
NK121(ko)004:244: stong nyid bsgoms pa dngos 'dzin gyi zhen pa grol phyir yin /
NK121(ko)004:245: de ma grol na stong nyid tshig tsam mo //
NK121(ko)004:246: 'dod pa la blo ma log pa'i bsgom byas pa la dgos pa med /
NK121(ko)004:247: mthar sgom chen grong chog la g.yeng ste tha mal du 'chi nyen yod /
NK121(ko)004:248: rang don dang mi ldan pa'i kha tshig bzang po la dgos pa med /
NK121(ko)004:249: lta ba kha khyer gyis bslus pa mang pas yin lugs gnad thog tu phobs /
NK121(ko)004:250: mos gus med pa la gdams ngag btab pa la dgos pa med do bu /
NK121(ko)004:251: nyams rtogs yon tan gang skyes bla ma'i byin rlabs
NK121(ko)004:252: la rag las mos gus med pa la byin rlabs
NK121(ko)004:255: dgos yod lnga yis snying rus dang go cha chen pos nyams su blang lugs bstan pa ni /
NK121(ko)004:256: dgos pa yod pa lnga la /
NK121(ko)004:257: bla ma la mos gus drag po byas na /
NK121(ko)004:258: brgyud pa'i byin rlabs shugs la 'go ba'i dgos pa yod /
NK121(ko)004:259: gsang sngags bya ba mos gus dang byin rlabs kyi lam pa yin /
NK121(ko)004:260: rtsa brgyud kyi bla ma rnams ngo bo gcig /
NK121(ko)004:261: sangs rgyas chos skur blta dgos /
NK121(ko)004:262: des sangs rgyas thams cad kyi byin rlabs 'jug pa yin /
NK121(ko)004:263: tshogs khyad par can bsags na ci bsam pa las su rung ba'i gos pa yod /
NK121(ko)004:264: bsod nams ldan pa'i mi yi bsam pa 'grub bya ba yin /
NK121(ko)004:265: dus rgyun du sems bskyed kyis zin pa'i yan lag bdun pa 'bul /
NK121(ko)004:266: des sems bzang po skye ba'i dgos pa yod /
NK121(ko)004:267: bsam pa las su rung na ting nge 'dzin khyad par can rgyud la skye ba'i dgos pa yod /
NK121(ko)004:268: lus sems las rung gi shin sbyang bsgom pa gal che /
NK121(ko)004:269: ting 'dzin khyad par can rgyud la skye na nyon mongs pa zil gyis gnon pa'i dgos pa yod /
NK121(ko)004:270: zhi gnas mgo gnon zhing lhag mthong gis sa bon drung nas 'byin no //
NK121(ko)004:271: nyon mongs med na byang chub myur du thob pa'i dgos pa yod do bu /
NK121(ko)004:272: rang sems sgrib pa dang bral ba de las byang chub gzhan na btsal du med do //
NK121(ko)004:274: chos 'dra chos min ngos bzung ba ni /
NK121(ko)004:276: 'jig rten la mngon par dga' bar byas nas skye shis 'jigs zer ba yang brdzun yin /
NK121(ko)004:277: chags bral mngon du ma byas par skye shi las grol ba'i skabs med /
NK121(ko)004:278: skye shis 'jigs pa med pas skyabs 'gro byed pa yang brdzun 'gro /
NK121(ko)004:279: tshig tsam gyis phan thog /'dod pa ma spangs par sgom chen yin zer yang brdzun du 'gro /
NK121(ko)004:280: phyi nang gang la'ang chags shing zhen pa de 'chings ba'i gzeb yin /
NK121(ko)004:281: gser sgrog dang thag sgrog 'ching byed du 'dra /
NK121(ko)004:282: las rgyu 'bras mi shes pa'i lta ba rtogs zer ba yang brdzun du 'gro /
NK121(ko)004:283: tshig tsam gyis phan mi thog /'dod pa ma spangs
NK121(ko)004:284: par sgom chen yin zer yang ma spangs par sangs
NK121(ko)004:285: rgyas yin zer ba'ang brdzun du 'agro'o bu /
NK121(ko)004:286: rgyu nyon mongs dug lnga ma spangs par 'bras bu srid pa'i g.yang sa mi khegs pas /
NK121(ko)004:287: gnyen po bslab gsum la brtson par bya'o //
NK121(ko)004:289: snying rus dang go cha thog bardzisa kyi ngang bsrings la nyams su blang ba ni /
NK121(ko)004:291: ma bsgom sangs rgyas mi 'ong zer ba bden /
NK121(ko)004:292: rang gis lam nyams su ma blang na sangs rgyas kyi phyag gis bzung yang mi phan /
NK121(ko)004:293: zhing 'di yang rnam snang gang sa chen mtsho'i phyag mthil na gnas pa yin /
NK121(ko)004:294: dam tshig ma nyams na dmyal bar mi 'gro zer ba bden /
NK121(ko)004:295: rtag tu rang sems dpang du btsug nas dran shes bzhin dang ma bral bar bya /
NK121(ko)004:296: thabs shes rab ya bral na nyan thos su lhung zer ba bden /
NK121(ko)004:297: theg chen la slob pas thabs shes ya ma bral bar bya /
NK121(ko)004:299: lta spyod zung 'jug ma shes na lam log zer ba bden /
NK121(ko)004:300: lta ba'i phyogs su spyod pa dang spyod pa'i phyogs su lta ba ma shor ba gces /
NK121(ko)004:301: sems rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa gsal ba la skyon ma dgos zer ba bden no //
NK121(ko)004:302: sems nyid rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba la glo
NK121(ko)004:303: bur gyi dri mas nam yang ma gos pas rang
NK121(ko)004:304: bzhin rnam dag chen por grub bo //
NK121(ko)004:305: de'i phyir lam la 'bad pa don yod pa yin gyi /
NK121(ko)004:306: gal te rang bzhin gyis ma dag na de dag
NK121(ko)004:307: par bsgyur du med pas lam la 'bad pa don
NK121(ko)004:310: byas kyang 'bras bu log pa ni /
NK121(ko)004:312: bcud dang mi ldan pa'i slob dpon bsten pa la don med /
NK121(ko)004:313: thog mar mtshan nyid brtag pa gal che /
NK121(ko)004:314: snod dang mi ldan pa'i slob bu bsten pa don med /
NK121(ko)004:315: lus dang grib ma bzhin 'grogs kyang gadamagasa ngag sbyin par mi bya /
NK121(ko)004:316: rang gzhan gnyis ka la phan mi thog /
NK121(ko)004:317: dam tshig mi bsrung ba'i mi dang 'brel ba byas pa don med /
NK121(ko)004:318: rang la nyams pa'i nyes pa 'go zhing de la'ang mi phan /
NK121(ko)004:319: sdig dang 'dres pa'i dge ba byas pa la don med /
NK121(ko)004:320: sbyor rjes sdig dang ma 'dres par bya dgos /
NK121(ko)004:321: 'dres ma'i las kyis bde sdug so sor smin pa la chos nyid yin /
NK121(ko)004:322: chos bzhin mi byed na chos shes pa don med do bu /
NK121(ko)004:323: de bas gang shes rang gi rgyud thog tu dril nas nyams su len pa gal che'o //
NK121(ko)004:325: gdams ngag snying rus dang go cha dang thog bardzisa kyis ngang bsrings la nyams su blang ba ni /
NK121(ko)004:327: bsgrub pa nyams su len na chags sdang gi la sgrol /
NK121(ko)004:328: thog mar chos brgyad cham la phob /
NK121(ko)004:329: thos pa gzhung bzhin byed na bzod pa go cha gyon /
NK121(ko)004:330: phyi dka' spyad dang nang zab mo'i don la mi skrag pa'i bzod pa la nan tan bya /
NK121(ko)004:331: gnas dang dgon par sdod na yid zas nor la
NK121(ko)004:332: ma 'jug /'dod chung chog shes brten pa gal che
NK121(ko)004:333: / zab mo'i chos 'dod na mkhas pa'i slob dpon bsten /
NK121(ko)004:334: go lo thos lor ma bzhag par gadamagasa ngag la sgro 'dogs chod par mdzod /
NK121(ko)004:335: mkhas nges pa'i slob dpon dang 'phrad na thugs ci ldog ma byed par thugs ci zin gyis /
NK121(ko)004:336: mkhas pa'i yon tan thams cad de las byung ngo //
NK121(ko)004:338: chos 'gag pa bab na mi phod pa bardzisa /
NK121(ko)004:339: lus srog thang la bor nas bla ma'i zhabs tog dang ro snyoms kyi spyod pa spyad /
NK121(ko)004:340: gnyen gyis skyug log na sems kyi 'khri ba chod /
NK121(ko)004:341: dgra gnyen ngo mnyam chags sdang rang grol la thongs /
NK121(ko)004:342: blo'i steng shor na shes pa bcud pa bor cig bu /
NK121(ko)004:343: blo yul thog tu shor na nyon mongs skye bas dad brtson dang dran shes kyi thag pas bzung /
NK121(ko)004:344: snying rus dang sdug bsran bskyed /
NK121(ko)004:345: gnyen po ye shes kyis 'khrul rtog rang grol gtong ba gnad yin no //
NK121(ko)004:347: sgrub pa nyams su len po'i 'phral gnas skabs gang du gang dgos su gzud par bstan pa ni /
NK121(ko)004:348: zhal chos sum cu rtsa bzhi la //
NK121(ko)004:349: phyi 'du 'dzi'i g.yeng bas dge sbyor g.yel /
NK121(ko)004:350: nang rnam rtog gi g.yeng bas nyon mongs ldang /
NK121(ko)004:351: bar mthu che byin rlabs kyi g.yeng bas rang srog la brgol ba'i phyir /
NK121(ko)004:352: bar chad 'byung gis g.yeng ba thongs //
NK121(ko)004:353: 'chi ba dug gi thug na phan med pas /
NK121(ko)004:354: sdod long med kyis myur du sgoms //
NK121(ko)004:356: so tshis ma mdzad shi tshis mdzod //
NK121(ko)004:357: dpe gzhon nu ma'i gdu bu dang 'dra /
NK121(ko)004:358: don g.yog la ma dga' gcig pur sgoms //
NK121(ko)004:359: khyad par du sdig grogs spongs /
NK121(ko)004:360: gnyen 'dun la chags pa rang sems kyi /
NK121(ko)004:361: 'khrul snang yin gyis bor la thongs //
NK121(ko)004:362: lus bya byed ngag smra brjod /
NK121(ko)004:363: sems rnam rtog gi /'byung 'jug ma mang rkyen ngan 'byung /
NK121(ko)004:364: ngo srung mthun 'jug sogs mi dgos pas /
NK121(ko)004:365: mi dang mi 'grog bde ba che //
NK121(ko)004:367: mi dang ma 'grogs chags sdang med /
NK121(ko)004:368: sems can rnams ni 'dod pas chog mi shes //
NK121(ko)004:369: thams cad sangs rgyas kyis kyang /
NK121(ko)004:370: mgu ba med pas ngo srung spongs //
NK121(ko)004:371: chags sdang gi rtogs pa med pa'i dpe /
NK121(ko)004:372: shi ba'i ro bzhin gcig pur sdod //
NK121(ko)004:373: chags sdang gi gnas spongs la chags med zhen med kyis /
NK121(ko)004:374: tsher khung ma 'gro bde sar sdod //
NK121(ko)004:375: de snga chags sdang gi phyogs su las srog btang ba /
NK121(ko)004:376: snga mas chog gi da ma gtong //
NK121(ko)004:377: da lus srog chos phyogs su thongs /
NK121(ko)004:378: sems can thams cad bde gshegs snying po'i rang bzhin can yin pas /
NK121(ko)004:379: dgra gnyen ma bzung ye shes zungs //
NK121(ko)004:380: mnyam pa nyid la nan tan bya /
NK121(ko)004:381: chos brgyad kyi ro myong ba sogs /
NK121(ko)004:382: grags snyan ma lta rang sems ltos //
NK121(ko)004:385: sdig sems skad cig ma res kyang ngan song du 'phen pa'i rgyu byed /
NK121(ko)004:386: thog med nas dngos 'dzin gyi zhen pas 'khor bar bcings bas /
NK121(ko)004:388: snga ma bzhin du 'khyams pa bor //
NK121(ko)004:389: 'phags pa'i nor gyi gtso bo 'am 'byung gnas chog shes yin pas /
NK121(ko)004:390: nor 'dod rgya mtsho'i gling du songs //
NK121(ko)004:391: chog shes med na rgyal po yin yang sprang po dang 'dra //
NK121(ko)004:392: zas gos srog 'tsho tsam gyis chog shes par byas te /
NK121(ko)004:393: gling du phyin ni phyir mi ldog /
NK121(ko)004:395: yo byad yod pa pha la phog /
NK121(ko)004:396: ci yod bla ma'i phyogs su phul la bla ma
NK121(ko)004:397: mnyes shing thugs zin na gdams ngag zab dgu 'byung
NK121(ko)004:398: bas / pha rgan mgu na snying gtam 'byung //
NK121(ko)004:400: snying gtam gsha' ma bu la smra //
NK121(ko)004:401: snod ldan gyi gdams ngag rdzogs par sbyin zhing /
NK121(ko)004:402: des kyang snying ltar bcings te nyams su len dgos pas /
NK121(ko)004:403: rin chen rnyed nas ma bor cig /'khor ba'i 'khrul snang la blo /
NK121(ko)004:404: log gis bzlog la drang por srong //
NK121(ko)004:405: ste byang chub kyi lam du songs /
NK121(ko)004:406: rdo rje'i spun dang sring 'tshogs na rang nyid kun las dman par lta dgos pas /
NK121(ko)004:407: ming sring 'tshogs na kha nyan sgrubs //
NK121(ko)004:409: stor gyi dogs na ra bar chug /
NK121(ko)004:412: bros kyis dogs na lcags kyus zungs /
NK121(ko)004:413: dran pa'i so ba brten dgos /
NK121(ko)004:414: cir snang chos skur shes pas rin chen gser gling du phyin pa lta bu'i gdeng gis /
NK121(ko)004:415: lta ba rang rkya tshugs par gyis //
NK121(ko)004:416: lha dang bla ma rang sems grogs kyis ma khrel pa'o //
NK121(ko)004:417: tshul khrims ngo lkog med par srungs //
NK121(ko)004:418: lan dang rnam smin la re ba spong ba'i /
NK121(ko)004:419: sbyin pa phyogs ris med par thongs //
NK121(ko)004:421: bzod pa rkyen ngan thub par gyis //
NK121(ko)004:422: chos phyir na tsha bkres skom sogs dang gzhan gyi
NK121(ko)004:423: sdug bsngal yang bdag gir dang du len dgos pas
NK121(ko)004:424: / thos bsam duhkhasa theg par gyis //
NK121(ko)004:425: snyan grags 'byung du re ba sogs /
NK121(ko)004:426: bsgom pa grags pa'i khar ma gtong //
NK121(ko)004:428: bdud kyis ma khyer spyod pa gyis //
NK121(ko)004:429: dus tshod dang 'brel ba gal che /
NK121(ko)004:430: snang ba yul phyir 'bring na rnam rtog dug lnga'i bdud ldang bas /
NK121(ko)004:431: snang ba bdud kyi slus pa yong ngo bu //
NK121(ko)004:432: des na sems yul phyir ma 'brang bar gces so //
NK121(ko)004:434: gdams pa drug gis nyes pa las bzlog par bstan pa ni /
NK121(ko)004:435: pha dang mes po'i rus ma 'tshong //
NK121(ko)004:436: rtsa ba'i bla ma dang brgyud pa'i rkang ma 'dren /
NK121(ko)004:437: spun dang pha spun dme ma byed //
NK121(ko)004:438: bla ma gcig pa dang rdo rje theg pa la
NK121(ko)004:439: zhugs pa'i mched la dam tshig mi bsrung ba'i 'thab
NK121(ko)004:440: rtsod spong / nye ring gzhan la rdul ma gtor //
NK121(ko)004:441: chos mdzad gzhan rnams tshig rtsub ma smra /
NK121(ko)004:442: rje la bca' ma phul ba'i 'bangs ma re //
NK121(ko)004:443: bla ma mnyes par ma byas pa la thugs rje dang byin rlabs mi 'byung /
NK121(ko)004:447: log pa'i lam ma mkhas shig bu //
NK121(ko)004:448: le'u bcu drug pa mi lto ba bcu'i yul rkyen bzang ngan theg par byed pa'i gdams pa ni /
NK121(ko)004:450: theg na zhes pa 'dam ka ste theg na khur mi theg na ma khur /
NK121(ko)004:451: mi lta zhes pa rkyen de dang des mi gnod pa na gyis /
NK121(ko)004:452: gnod na ma byed ces pa'i don yin pas yul
NK121(ko)004:453: can ngan pa thams cad kyis mi gnod par lam
NK121(ko)004:455: yul gyi nad theg na yul du bsdad kyang mi sto /
NK121(ko)004:456: dgra gnyen la chags sdang mi skye bas /
NK121(ko)004:457: 'brel ba'i nad theg na gnyen na ma bral yang mi lto /
NK121(ko)004:458: sgegs chos ngo tsha sogs kyi shub nas thon te /
NK121(ko)004:459: gos kyi nad theg na gcer bur byas kyang mi lto /
NK121(ko)004:460: skyid sdug ro mnyam lam du khyer nus pas /
NK121(ko)004:461: chags sdang gi nad theg na spyod pa byas kyang mi lto /
NK121(ko)004:462: rang sems bla mar rtogs nas tha dad kyi mtshan 'dzin rang sar grol bas /
NK121(ko)004:463: bla ma'i nad theg na mos gus kyi 'phro bcad kyang mi lto /
NK121(ko)004:464: 'khor 'das ming med cir snang rang byung gi ye shes su rtogs pas /
NK121(ko)004:465: 'khor ba'i nad theg na chos byas mi lto /
NK121(ko)004:466: snang sems chos nyid grol te bag chags kyi rjes med pas /
NK121(ko)004:467: ngan song gi nad theg na sdig pa byas kyang mi lto //
NK121(ko)004:468: gzhan don du gang yang spyod pas chog /
NK121(ko)004:469: chos nyid bya rtsol dang bral bas /
NK121(ko)004:470: ngo bo tha dad du shar yang /
NK121(ko)004:471: dam tshig bsrung mtshams las 'das shing 'khor 'das rang sems su shes pas /
NK121(ko)004:472: dmyal ba'i nad theg na gsang sngags kyi sgor zhugs nas dam tshig ma bsrung yang mi lto /
NK121(ko)004:473: byas chos 'khrul pas shes te byar med blo 'das kyi /
NK121(ko)004:474: lta ba'i gdeng yod na cog ge nyal yang mi lto /
NK121(ko)004:475: gnas khang bzang ngan gyi zhen 'dzin med pas /
NK121(ko)004:476: gnas kyi nad theg na gang du bsdad kyang mi lto /
NK121(ko)004:477: zas la bzang ngan med cing gtsang rme gnyis 'dzin dang bral bas /
NK121(ko)004:478: lto ba'i nad theg na ci zos kyang mi lto /
NK121(ko)004:479: bdag gces 'dzin gyi khri ba chod pas /
NK121(ko)004:480: las kyi nad theg na 'gos nad la ma 'dzems kyang mi lto'o bu //
NK121(ko)004:482: chos pa spyi dang rang gi skyon brtag pa rgya gad 'cha' ba ste /
NK121(ko)004:484: spyir rgya gad dang log chus dang blun pa dang
NK121(ko)004:485: dam tshig nyams pa'i skyon rnams mi 'byung ba'i rgyu
NK121(ko)004:486: brgyad yod do // mi gzhi legs pas 'khrid btub pa /
NK121(ko)004:488: 'chi ba rjes su dran pas tshe phyi ma don du gnyer ba /
NK121(ko)004:489: bde sdug las 'bras su yid ches pas sdig la 'dzem /
NK121(ko)004:493: tshig btsun pas khas len las mi 'gal bar blo gtad thub pa'o //
NK121(ko)004:494: de'i ldog phyogs kyis skyon brgyad yod pa la /
NK121(ko)004:498: mi chos lha chos gnyis ka nas khrel ba'o //
NK121(ko)004:500: dad pa skyes te gnas la mchong la khad /
NK121(ko)004:501: chos zhu dus skra 'bal ba dang ngu ba sogs mi phyed dgu gcig byed /
NK121(ko)004:502: bar du the tshom zos nas lung stong rjes kyis bkang /
NK121(ko)004:503: gdams ngag sgro 'dogs ma chod par the tshom skyes te phyogs kun nyul /
NK121(ko)004:504: tha ma dad pa log nas dmyal ba'i gting rdo byed /
NK121(ko)004:505: mthar chos dang bla ma la log lta skyes pa ste dad pa mi brtan pa'i skyon gsum mo //
NK121(ko)004:506: dang po slob dpon rnyed nas ci bya'i lung khung mang /
NK121(ko)004:507: blo snying brang gsum gtad nas nged kyi bla ma'i
NK121(ko)004:508: zab chos gsung gi gces pa zhes gsang ba kun
NK121(ko)004:509: la sgrogs / bar du slob dpon sun nas sgro dang skur ba 'debs /
NK121(ko)004:510: sngar phul ba la 'gyod cing skyon mtshangs sgrogs /
NK121(ko)004:511: tha ma slob dpon bor nas dgra yi dam par 'dzin /
NK121(ko)004:512: gsar 'grogs kyis gzhan bsten pa ste slob dpon brten lugs nyes pa'i skyon gsum mo //
NK121(ko)004:513: dang po sems 'dzin byung nas chos pa nga las med /
NK121(ko)004:514: zhi gnas kyi nyams than thun skyes pa la snyems
NK121(ko)004:515: nas sgom chen dang chos pa bya ba rang las
NK121(ko)004:517: bar du bsgom pas sun nas brtson bu gnya' med 'dra /
NK121(ko)004:518: dgon par nyin skyo mtshan 'jigs shing nub za nyal la dga'/
NK121(ko)004:519: tha ma bsgom pa bor nas grong khyer nyul le ma /
NK121(ko)004:521: don kun rdzob khyad du gsod byed pa ste /
NK121(ko)004:522: nyams len gzhung ma srong ba'i skyon gsum mo /
NK121(ko)004:523: dang po nyams len skyes pas ras chod spyod pa byed /
NK121(ko)004:525: don kun rdzob khyad du gsod /
NK121(ko)004:526: bar du bsgom pa bor nas yig sna'i rtsal bshad byed /
NK121(ko)004:527: dpe rang la lam rgyus med par gzhan la ston pa dang 'dra /
NK121(ko)004:528: rang la go rtogs med par gzhan la bshad /
NK121(ko)004:529: tha ma phung po 'bor khar tha mal ngang du 'chi //
NK121(ko)004:530: dpe skye bo tha mal pa ltar /
NK121(ko)004:531: don 'chi khar lam sna ma zin pa ste nyams
NK121(ko)004:532: myong la brtan pa ma thong ba'i skyon gsum mo
NK121(ko)004:533: // dang po lta ba rtogs pa'i nges shes bag tsam skyes /
NK121(ko)004:534: don spyi'i go yul tsam rnyed pa rtogs pa bzang por rlom /
NK121(ko)004:536: bar du the tshom zos pas shes brdzun gzhan la 'dri /
NK121(ko)004:537: ye shes shes brdzun byas nas gzhan la 'dri btsug byed /
NK121(ko)004:538: tha ma lta ba 'gyangs bas gol sgrib dbang du shor /
NK121(ko)004:539: mu stegs dang cha 'dra rtag chad kyi dbang du
NK121(ko)004:540: shor nas zung 'jug spros bral mnyam pa nyid ma
NK121(ko)004:541: rtogs pa ste rtogs pa'i gdeng ma rnyed pa'i skyon
NK121(ko)004:542: gsum mo // 'bras bu gol sar song bas thar pa'i skar khung 'gags /
NK121(ko)004:543: thabs shes sogs zung du ma chud cing lam gnad 'chol bas 'bras bu myang 'das sgo 'gags /
NK121(ko)004:544: thar pa'i skar khung 'gags pas skye shi rgyun mi chad /
NK121(ko)004:545: cir snang dngos por bzung zhing lus sems la bdag
NK121(ko)004:546: tu bzung ba'i dbang gis las nyon gyis rang bcing
NK121(ko)004:547: ste mi thar / skye shi rgyun mi chad pas skye gnas la 'dam dbang med do bya /
NK121(ko)004:548: las nyon gyi dbang gis rang dbang med par srid
NK121(ko)004:549: par nying mtshams sbyor ba ste 'bras bu phyin log
NK121(ko)004:550: tu gyur ba'i skyon nam rgya gad gsum mo //
NK121(ko)004:551: des chos dang rang sems ma 'dres pa'i skyon rnams ngos bzung nas spong ba la 'bad par bya'o //
NK121(ko)004:553: log chos bco lnga'i sgo nas gol sgrib kyi mtha' bcad pa ni /
NK121(ko)004:554: lha chos las log nas mi chos su song yang cha lugs lha chos su gnas pas /
NK121(ko)004:556: lta ba g.yo ma la rgyugs /
NK121(ko)004:557: gzhan gyi kha rgyug byas te rang rgyud ma thul /
NK121(ko)004:558: sgom pa glen sgom du shor /
NK121(ko)004:559: lhag mthong med pas nyon mongs gzhi rtsad nas ma chod de nyams rtogs ma skyes /
NK121(ko)004:561: chos min la spyod pas smyon pa dang 'dra /
NK121(ko)004:562: bsags sbyang gi gnad mi shes /
NK121(ko)004:563: dam tshig tshod yod du shor /
NK121(ko)004:564: bsrung mtshams mi shes shing 'di tsam nyams kyang sla zhes khyad du gsod /
NK121(ko)004:565: slob dpon rang cag gi 'brel la byed /
NK121(ko)004:566: rang gi a khu'am a zhang lta bur bzung nas dad gus mi bskyed pa /
NK121(ko)004:567: nyan pa ngo log tu nyan /
NK121(ko)004:568: gzhan gyi ngo bsrung dang mi'i 'phya dogs su nyan
NK121(ko)004:569: pas chos mi go bsgrub pa dal khom du 'jog
NK121(ko)004:570: / gnyid dang snyom las kyi dbang du song bas 'bras bu mi thob /
NK121(ko)004:574: 'bras bu 'jig rten pa'i grags pa bsgrub /
NK121(ko)004:575: chos brgyad kyi chags sdang rgyas /
NK121(ko)004:576: tha mal pa dang khyad med /
NK121(ko)004:577: gdams ngag gzu lum du len /
NK121(ko)004:578: zhabs tog dang nyams len med par dpe yod dang lung thob tsam la brten /
NK121(ko)004:579: des nyams myong gi rdo rus mi 'phrod /
NK121(ko)004:580: 'dzam bu gling gi mi lus thob nas stong log byed /
NK121(ko)004:581: dpe rin po che'i gling nas stong log byas pa dang 'dra /
NK121(ko)004:582: chos pa'i mal nas tha mal pa'i ro byung /
NK121(ko)004:583: mi lus thob pa don med du song /
NK121(ko)004:585: de dus 'gyod kyang bya thabs zad /
NK121(ko)004:587: chos ma byas na ming chos par btags kyang mi phan /
NK121(ko)004:588: chos min spyod na ming dge bshes zer yang sdig bshes su song ba yin /
NK121(ko)004:590: bro glu'i bstod sgra la nyan pa bzhin snyan grags
NK121(ko)004:591: ngo bstod zer lo skam po nyan pas mi yong
NK121(ko)004:592: / mi tshe stong zad du rgyur nyen /
NK121(ko)004:594: shi nas dmyal ba las 'os med do bu /
NK121(ko)004:595: de thams cad kyi rtsa ba tshe 'di la chags
NK121(ko)004:596: shing zhen pa las byung bas skyon ngos bzung la
NK121(ko)004:597: spang bar bya'o // le'u bcu dgu pa /
NK121(ko)004:598: blun pa nyi shu rtsa drug gi sgo nas brod sdigs kyi mtha' bstan pa ni /
NK121(ko)004:599: mi chos kyi blun pa nyer drug la dpe byas nas /
NK121(ko)004:601: blun pa nyi shu rtsa drug la /
NK121(ko)004:602: yong nges pa'i dmag la mi 'jigs pa blun /
NK121(ko)004:604: chags nges pa'i bu lon mi 'jal ba blun /
NK121(ko)004:605: lan chags sdig sgrib mi sbyang ba /
NK121(ko)004:606: 'dzin nges pa'i dgra khar 'gro ba blun /
NK121(ko)004:608: mi theg pa'i khur 'khur ba la dga' bas blun /
NK121(ko)004:609: sdig pa'i rnam smin la mi 'dzem pa /
NK121(ko)004:610: skyid med pa'i gnas su 'gro ba la brod pa blun /
NK121(ko)004:611: sdig pa'i phyogs la dga' ba /
NK121(ko)004:612: 'chi nges pa'i g.yang sa la 'chong ba blun /
NK121(ko)004:614: sa bon bra bo la byas nas 'bras bu nas re ba blun /
NK121(ko)004:615: sdig pa byas pa'i 'bras bu bde ba 'byung du re ba /
NK121(ko)004:616: brag phug kha byang bltas su nyi ma 'char du re bas blun /
NK121(ko)004:617: rang la mos gus med par bla ma'i byin rlabs 'byung bar re ba /
NK121(ko)004:618: bslu nges pa la re ba dang ltos pa 'jog pas blun /
NK121(ko)004:619: tshe 'di'i phun sum tshogs la zhen pa /
NK121(ko)004:620: gnod bu rgyal bu can la 'dren pas blun /
NK121(ko)004:621: bran bu rgyal bur 'gran pa bzhin rang tha mal du sdod par yon tan 'byung du re ba /
NK121(ko)004:622: yo byad med par phyug por re bas blun /
NK121(ko)004:623: rang la yon tan med par gzhan gyi slob dpon du re ba /
NK121(ko)004:624: mi chags par rta la zhon pa blun /
NK121(ko)004:625: mi thub pa la dam bca' byed pa /
NK121(ko)004:626: las ma byas par zin la skad zer ba blun /
NK121(ko)004:627: gnas lugs ma rtogs par thabs khyad du bsad pa /
NK121(ko)004:628: nad ma sos par sman pa la mi mgu bar dug sdud pa la yid du 'ongs pa blun /
NK121(ko)004:629: dug lnga'i nad gso ba'i sman pa la mi mos pa sdig grogs la mos pa /
NK121(ko)004:630: tshang pa zong med par za la dga' bas blun /
NK121(ko)004:631: rang la go rtogs med par gzhan la bshad pa /
NK121(ko)004:632: phas zhal ta byas pa mi nyan par rbad pa bzhin du 'gro ba blun /
NK121(ko)004:633: bla ma'i gdams ngag mi nyan par phyin ci log tu 'gro ba /
NK121(ko)004:634: bud med blo nyes ma bu'i bcas pas bu mo'i bcas la dga' ba blun /
NK121(ko)004:635: phyi ma'i chos las tshe 'di'i 'dod yon la dga' ba /
NK121(ko)004:636: gcer bur khyim nas thon nas gos rnyed nas khyim du log nas 'ong ba blun /
NK121(ko)004:637: chos shes nas chos mi byed par nor bsgrub pa /
NK121(ko)004:638: chu ma thon par lham 'bud pa blun /
NK121(ko)004:639: rtogs pa'i gdeng dang mi bar chos spyod rgyun gcod pa /
NK121(ko)004:640: mi ngoms par lan tsha'i chu la 'thung ba blun /
NK121(ko)004:641: 'dod pa la chog shes med pa /
NK121(ko)004:642: phyi zhig pa nang gis ma tshor ba blun /
NK121(ko)004:643: lus rgas kyang sems chags sdang che ba /
NK121(ko)004:644: gzhan la gros 'debs pa mkhas kyang rang gi 'dun ma log par gtang bas blun /
NK121(ko)004:645: rang gi kha bshad dang lag len 'dzol ba /
NK121(ko)004:646: skas med par mi thar ba'i rdzong la 'dzeg pa blun /
NK121(ko)004:647: tshogs ma rdzogs par thar bar 'gro bar rlom /
NK121(ko)004:648: byis pa rnams 'ongs nges pa'i las byed du mi 'dod pas blun /
NK121(ko)004:649: las dang po pas dge sbyor phyi bshol du 'jog pa /
NK121(ko)004:650: mi thar ba'i chu la sgrol ba la yid mi 'tsher bas blun /
NK121(ko)004:651: skye rga na 'chis mi 'tsher ba sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa /
NK121(ko)004:652: rang la bzhag nas gzhan du tshol bas blun no bu /
NK121(ko)004:653: mdor na de thams cad kyang /
NK121(ko)004:655: rgyu med kyi 'bras bu 'dod pa dang /
NK121(ko)004:656: bla ma'i gsung la mi nyan pa dang /
NK121(ko)004:657: lha chos par khas blangs nas mi chos skyong ba /
NK121(ko)004:658: bshad pa dang lag len 'gal ba'i skyon te lngar 'dus so //
NK121(ko)004:660: zhal gdams dgu pa'i sgo nas rang rgyud kyi gyong bcag pa ni /
NK121(ko)004:661: 7 zhal lung snying la bcang bya yin pas zhal gdams te /
NK121(ko)004:664: thub pa'i rnam thar ltos la rang nyid de'i rjes su slob /
NK121(ko)004:665: lkog rmugs yi dam la gyis /
NK121(ko)004:666: dus rgyun ma brjed par bsnyen sgrub la brtson /
NK121(ko)004:667: gnag pa gdams ngag la gyis /
NK121(ko)004:668: gsang zhing sgrub na byin rlabs dang nyams rtogs 'phral du 'byung /
NK121(ko)004:669: gzhung ngan sdig pa la gyis /
NK121(ko)004:670: mi dge ba dang de spyod pa'i grogs la phyi mig mi blta /
NK121(ko)004:671: gtong phod bla ma'i phyogs su gyis /
NK121(ko)004:672: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas mchod pa bas don che /
NK121(ko)004:674: rang sems rtsad chod la phyis 'khor bar mi skye ba'i thabs la brtson /
NK121(ko)004:676: rang mtshangs ngan pa yul nas thon /
NK121(ko)004:679: mdo rgyud bal bzhin g.yengs shig bu /
NK121(ko)004:680: thos pa phyogs med du btsal zhing rang rgyud la
NK121(ko)004:681: sbyar te chos dang rang sems zhu dag bya ba
NK121(ko)004:682: gal che'o // le'u nyer gcig pa /
NK121(ko)004:683: snying gtam dgu'i sgo nas rang dman pa'i cha gzung ba ni /
NK121(ko)004:686: sgom chen ri dang ma bral na yon tan zhag skyed kyi 'phel /
NK121(ko)004:688: gyong lto gos gtam gsum la bskur dgos /
NK121(ko)004:690: mi chos rlung la ma bskur na chags sdang mkhar po mi zhig /
NK121(ko)004:692: chags zhen med cing sgrub sla /
NK121(ko)004:693: mang po'i gseb nas gcig pur bros /
NK121(ko)004:694: 'phral dge sbyor 'phel bar chad mi 'byung 'tsho ba zhar la yong /
NK121(ko)004:696: gdung sems blos ma thongs na 'khri ba mi chod /
NK121(ko)004:697: sna thag mi la ma shor /
NK121(ko)004:699: mi blo dang chu sna gar khel du 'gro bas rang sems dran pa'i thag pa zungs /
NK121(ko)004:701: 'khor ba'i bde ba la ma chags /
NK121(ko)004:702: 'di ma bor na sdig sdug gtam ngan rgyud mi 'chad /
NK121(ko)004:703: blo phug nam mkha' la gtod cig bu /
NK121(ko)004:704: bdag med gnyis kyi don la goms 'dris bya ba gal che'o //
NK121(ko)004:706: bde ba lnga'i sgo nas rkyen bzang ngan snyom par khyer ba'i gdams ngag ni /
NK121(ko)004:709: dug sdong sus shes skyes bu bde //
NK121(ko)004:710: sdug bsngal rang bzhin yin par shes nas spongs /
NK121(ko)004:711: nyon mongs skye ba'i rgyu rnams la //
NK121(ko)004:712: dge bshes yin par sus mthong bde //
NK121(ko)004:713: dgra mthong na bzod pa skye ba'i slob dpon yin pa lta bus mtshon no //
NK121(ko)004:714: shes rab gsum sbyong slob dpon la //
NK121(ko)004:715: legs par mthong ba'i skyes bu bde //
NK121(ko)004:716: bla ma sangs rgyas dang gdams ngag bdud rtsir shes
NK121(ko)004:717: pa des gtan du thar pa'i lam sna zin pa
NK121(ko)004:718: yin / phyi nang dngos can thams cad la //
NK121(ko)004:719: skye ba med pas sus mthong ba de /
NK121(ko)004:720: des sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa longs pa yin /
NK121(ko)004:721: bya ba thams cad phyir bshol nas /
NK121(ko)004:722: ma nor lam la zhugs na bade'o bu /
NK121(ko)004:723: mdor na tshe 'di'i bya ba thams cad btang nas
NK121(ko)004:724: yang dag pa'i gdams ngag nyams su longs na bde
NK121(ko)004:725: skyid kyi nyi ma sems la 'char nges so //
NK121(ko)004:727: mdo sngags gnyis kyi so mtshams su dam tshig nyams pa'i rgyu nyi shu la 'dzem pa ni /
NK121(ko)004:728: 7 dam tshig nyams pa'i rgyu nyi shu la /
NK121(ko)004:729: gnas skabs dgos dbang lta bu ma yin par snying thag pa nas /
NK121(ko)004:730: slob dpon gsang nas rang gi che ba'i yon tan brjod na dam tshig nyams pa'i rgyu /
NK121(ko)004:731: dgag bya dgos pa med bzhin /
NK121(ko)004:732: mkhas pa dang mi mkhas pa mnyam par blta na dam tshig nyams pa'i rgyu /
NK121(ko)004:734: yon bdag dang slob ma gnyis ka 'gran na dam tshig nyams pa'i rgyu /
NK121(ko)004:735: rang dbang yod bzhin bla ma la nor longs spyod sogs /
NK121(ko)004:736: dbul bar bsam zhing bshol na dam tshig nyams pa'i rgyu /
NK121(ko)004:737: brgyud pa la sel yod med sogs mi rtog par /
NK121(ko)004:738: chos thos tshad du zhu na dam tshig nyams pa'i rgyu /
NK121(ko)004:739: yang na 'di la rnam bshad du chos thub chos
NK121(ko)004:740: su zhu na zhes gsungs te chos gang zhu na'ang
NK121(ko)004:741: thog mar bla ma'i thugs dang bstun dgos /
NK121(ko)004:742: dus su ma babs bzhin du dbang yod dang byas yus kyis /
NK121(ko)004:743: gdams pa nan gyis len na dam tshig nyams pa'i rgyu /
NK121(ko)004:745: bla dang mched grogs bslu na dam tshig nyams pa'i rgyu /
NK121(ko)004:747: ngan skyon slob dpon la 'gel na dam tshig nyams pa'i rgyu /
NK121(ko)004:749: slob dpon la zhe 'dren na dam tshig nyams pa'i rgyu /
NK121(ko)004:750: gsang ba gnyer gtad la gzhan la 'khyal ba'am rang skyon bla ma la gsang ba ste /
NK121(ko)004:751: slob dpon la gsang 'khun dam tshig nyams pa'i rgyu /
NK121(ko)004:752: nus pa yod bzhin du mi gzo bar /
NK121(ko)004:753: bka' drin khyad du gsod na dam tshig nyams pa'i rgyu /
NK121(ko)004:754: rang 'dod ha cang che drag pa dang rang mthong nga rgyal gyis /
NK121(ko)004:755: rang gis don mthong drag na dam tshig nyams pa'i rgyu /
NK121(ko)004:756: bla ma dang mched la ma zhus par lkog tu
NK121(ko)004:757: 'bri ba dang lhag par dpe dngos brkus te rtsad
NK121(ko)004:758: bcad pa ste / gdams pa dpe rkun byed na dam tshig nyams pa'i rgyu /
NK121(ko)004:759: bla ma bla ma'i 'khor gyi skyon mtshangs te /
NK121(ko)004:760: slob dpon barngana lkog tu bgrang na dam tshig nyams pa'i rgyu /
NK121(ko)004:761: dad can sun phyung ba ste /
NK121(ko)004:762: gzhan gyi mos pa bzlog na dam tshig nyams pa'i rgyu /
NK121(ko)004:763: dus min du gsang spyod byed pa ste /
NK121(ko)004:764: nang spyod phyir 'don na dam tshig nyams pa'i rgyu /
NK121(ko)004:766: rdo rje'i spun la phrag dog byed na dam tshig nyams pa'i rgyu /
NK121(ko)004:767: rang gis ma thos pa'am thob kyang bkas ma gnang bar rang dgar spyod pa ste /
NK121(ko)004:768: bla ma dang gdams ngag med par ras chod byed na dam tshig nyams pa'i rgyu /
NK121(ko)004:769: rang gi mi shes shing rna brgyud med par rang bzos rtsal bshad byed pa ste /
NK121(ko)004:770: gzu lum du bshad na dam tshig nyams pa'i rgyu /
NK121(ko)004:771: sdang zhen gyis mu stegs can la'ang mi smad par gsungs na gzhan la lta ci smos /
NK121(ko)004:773: chos dang chos pa la skur pa 'debs na dam tshig nyams pa'i rgyu /
NK121(ko)004:774: theg dman sogs la gsang ba sgra ji bzhin par ston pa ste /
NK121(ko)004:775: snod min la gdams ngag logs su btab na dam tshig nyams pa'i rgyu'o bu /
NK121(ko)004:776: gzhan yang rtsa ba dang yan lag gi bsrung bya'i rnam grangs dang /
NK121(ko)004:779: bsrung ba'i phan yon rnams shes par byas nas dran
NK121(ko)004:780: shes dang bag yod kyis rtag tu brtson par bya'o
NK121(ko)004:782: / 7 / de rnams kyi sgo nas stod dad can chos la dwangs pa bskyed cing /
NK121(ko)004:783: sde snod spyi dang mthun par lhag pa tshul khrims
NK121(ko)004:784: kyi bslab pa la brten nas bsgrub pa'i gzhi bca'
NK121(ko)004:785: bas rang rgyud 'dul bar byed pa ma bu 'khrid
NK121(ko)004:786: cing skyong ba lta bu'i gdams ngag thal lo //
NK121(ko)004:787: zhal gyi gdams pa brgyad cu pa las /
NK121(ko)004:788: gzhi tshul khrims rnam par dag pa la gdams pa'i skabs te gnyis pa'o //
NK121(ko)004:789: rtsa ba'i sa bcad gsum pa //
NK121(ko)004:790: thabs rnam par dag pa lhag pa sems kyi lhag la gdams pa la /
NK121(ko)004:791: le'u bcu bdun du bzhugs pa las /
NK121(ko)004:792: le'u nyer bzhi pa byin brlabs bzhi'i sgo nas sgom pa'i grogs bstan pa ni /
NK121(ko)004:795: gdams ngag gi zab khyad gsum 'dzoms pas /
NK121(ko)004:796: nyams myong btsan thabs su skyed par byed par /
NK121(ko)004:797: byin rlabs kyi lag len bzhi la /
NK121(ko)004:798: rang sems chos nyid du shes pas yul thams cad
NK121(ko)004:799: chos nyid du grol te yul rkyen gyis mi gnod
NK121(ko)004:800: pa / lham mthil gyi dpes mtshon nas bdag byin gyis rlobs pa dang /
NK121(ko)004:801: chos thams cad rang byung gi ye shes su ngo 'phrod pas glo bur gyi mtshan ma med pa /
NK121(ko)004:802: ri gzar shwa bud kyi dpes mtshon nas snang ba byin gyis rlobs pa dang /
NK121(ko)004:803: ting nge 'dzin rtse gcig pas rgyun chad med pa /
NK121(ko)004:804: chu bo'i gzhung gi dpes mtshon nas sems byin gyis rlobs pa dang /
NK121(ko)004:805: ce spyang nag po'i mig gis nyin mtshan med par
NK121(ko)004:806: mthong ba ltar gzung 'dzin gnyis med du ngo sprod
NK121(ko)004:807: pa / ce spyang gi dpes mtshon nas gnyis med du byin gyis rlob pa'o bu /
NK121(ko)004:811: gnyis med rang grol du shes pas phyi nang gnang ba de kho na nyid kyi sgro 'dogs chod /
NK121(ko)004:812: 'on kyang rang blo chos nyid du ma grol na
NK121(ko)004:813: yin pa tsam gyis mi phan te 'khyags pa chu
NK121(ko)004:814: yis kyang ma zhu na chu'i bya ba mi byed
NK121(ko)004:815: pa bzhin / des na mos gus drag pos bsgom pa gal che'o //
NK121(ko)004:816: da lta lam pa'i rnal 'byor pas rang sems kyi chos nyid mngon sum rtogs kyang /
NK121(ko)004:817: chos can thams cad chos nyid du grol ba min
NK121(ko)004:818: pas brgya phrag bcu gnyis sogs kyis yon tan dngos
NK121(ko)004:820: rim gyis goms pas chos can thams cad chos nyid
NK121(ko)004:821: du grol ba'am thim pa'i tshe mthar phyin sangs rgyas
NK121(ko)004:822: kyi sa yi bar gyi yon tan rnams mngon gyur
NK121(ko)004:824: des na da lta so skye'i skabs kyi rtog pa la /
NK121(ko)004:826: sa thob yan gyi rtogs pa la 'grib pa med 'phel ba yod /
NK121(ko)004:827: sangs rgyas kyi sa na gnyis ka med gsungs //
NK121(ko)004:829: lam khyer dpe don gyis bsgom pa'i grogs bstan pa ni /
NK121(ko)004:830: lam khyer gyi gdams ngag bzhi la /
NK121(ko)004:832: zang zing phyir ni duhkha ste //
NK121(ko)004:833: zang zing med na bde ba'i mchog /
NK121(ko)004:834: zang zing yongs su spangs pa las //
NK121(ko)004:837: skyar mo nya khyer gyi dpes mtshon nas zhen med lam khyer ba la /
NK121(ko)004:838: nyon mongs ye shes su shar bas /
NK121(ko)004:839: dug la sngags btab kyi dpes mtshon nas dug lnga lam du khyer ba dang /
NK121(ko)004:840: tshogs brgyad skye med du shes pas srid rtsa bdag 'dzin chod pa /
NK121(ko)004:841: ljon shing rtsa bcad kyi dpes mtshon nas tshogs brgyad kyi skye med du lam du khyer ba dang /
NK121(ko)004:842: chos kyis skye med la mtshan ma'i chos kyis gos su med pas /
NK121(ko)004:843: 'dam skyes pad+ma'i dpes mtshon nas dag pa chen por lam du khyer ro bu //
NK121(ko)004:845: shes bya dpe don gyi sgo nas bsgom pa grogs dang bcas pa ni /
NK121(ko)004:846: 7 shes bya bzhi'i gdams ngag la /
NK121(ko)004:847: snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos kun bden pas stong pa /
NK121(ko)004:848: sgyu ma mkhan gyi dpes mtshon nas zhen med du shes par bya /
NK121(ko)004:849: chos thams cad rang bzhin gnyis su med pas /
NK121(ko)004:850: tsan+da gla ba'i dpes mtshon nas gnyis med du shes par bya /
NK121(ko)004:851: 'dus byas mtshan ma'i chos la yid brtan med pas /
NK121(ko)004:852: grogs po mdza' bos bslus pa'i dpes mtshon nas gnyen 'dun gyis bslu bar shes par bya /
NK121(ko)004:853: ye nas chos nyid rang la rang chas su yod pas /
NK121(ko)004:854: til dang sgron me'i dpes mtshon nas 'du 'bral med par bya'o bu /
NK121(ko)004:855: de ltar shes na bden zhen gnyis 'dzin gyi 'ching
NK121(ko)004:856: ba rang sar grol ba'i shes rab dri med rgyud
NK121(ko)004:857: la skye'o // le'u nyer bdun pa /
NK121(ko)004:858: bsgom pa grogs dang bcas pa ston pa ni /
NK121(ko)004:859: 7 gnad kyi gdams ngag bzhi la /
NK121(ko)004:860: chos nyid stong pa'i rtsal sna tshogs su shar yang
NK121(ko)004:861: shar dus nas rang bzhin med pas snang stong zung
NK121(ko)004:862: du 'jug pa / dngul dkar me long phyis pa'i
NK121(ko)004:863: dpes mtshon nas snang ba ma 'gags pa chig chod
NK121(ko)004:864: du ston pa'i gdams ngag gi gnad /
NK121(ko)004:865: gnyis med la gnyis su 'dzin pas ma bcing bar mtshan ma rang sar grol ba /
NK121(ko)004:866: brtson bkrol ba'i dpes mtshon nas mtshan mas ma bsdams pas gdams ngag gi gnad /
NK121(ko)004:867: rang sems skye med kyi don la bsgom rgyu rdul
NK121(ko)004:868: tsam med kyang yengs su skad gcig med par blo
NK121(ko)004:870: mda' bsrang ba dang 'ben la 'phen pa'i dpes mtshon
NK121(ko)004:871: nas don skye med la ma yengs pa gdams ngag
NK121(ko)004:872: gi gnad / nam mkha' sum phrug gi dgongs pas
NK121(ko)004:873: dbyings rig 'du 'bral med pa'i don las mi g.yo
NK121(ko)004:874: gi gnad / ba / mig 'byed sman pa'i dpes
NK121(ko)004:875: mtshon nas dmigs pa rtse gcig tu bzhag pa'i gdams
NK121(ko)004:876: ngag gi gnad dgos so bu /
NK121(ko)004:877: des 'khrul snang gzhi med du sangs nas mtshan ma rang sar grol bar 'gyur ro //
NK121(ko)004:879: phyi nang gi spros pa gcod pa'i zhal gdams ni /
NK121(ko)004:881: mtshan rtog gang shar chos nyid las gzhan du 'da' sa med pa /
NK121(ko)004:882: rus sbal dngul gzhong du bzhag pa'i dpes mtshon nas mtshan ma'i 'byung 'jug rgyun bcad /
NK121(ko)004:883: cir snang chos nyid las ma g.yos pa /
NK121(ko)004:884: gser las bzo byas pa'i dpes mtshon nas rang bzhin chos nyid las mi 'da' bar thag bcad /
NK121(ko)004:885: bde sdug sna tshogs rig pa'i ngang du gcig pa /
NK121(ko)004:886: bu ram dang mngar ba'i dpes mtshon nas gnyis su med par thag bcad /
NK121(ko)004:887: 'khor 'das thams cad rang byung ye shes kyi rtsal las shar ba /
NK121(ko)004:888: chu zla dang nam mkha'i zla ba'i dpes mtshon nas rig pa rang byung du thag bcad do bu //
NK121(ko)004:890: 'khor 'das kyi byus gdab pa'i sgo nas bsgom pa'i grogs bstan pa ni /
NK121(ko)004:892: ngo bo zung du chud pas rol pa brgyan du bkod pa /
NK121(ko)004:893: 'ja' tshon nam mkha'i rgyan gyi dpes mtshon nas dran snang chos nyid kyi rgyan du lta ba /
NK121(ko)004:894: rnam rtog chos nyid du shes pas chags sdang gi srog chod pa /
NK121(ko)004:895: ral gri ngar blud kyi dpes mtshon nas rnam rtog chos nyid du lta ba /
NK121(ko)004:896: bag chags kyi rjes mi gsog pa /
NK121(ko)004:897: mkha' la bya 'phur gyi dpes mtshon nas dran snang rjes med du lta ba /
NK121(ko)004:898: chos can chos kyi nyid du grol ba /
NK121(ko)004:899: rmi lam gnyid sad kyi dpes mtshon nas snang srid mi bden par lta ba'o bu //
NK121(ko)004:901: bzhag thabs dngos bstan pa ni /
NK121(ko)004:904: ting nge 'dzin gyi rgyu tshogs tshang zhing bzhag thabs kyi gnad la mkhas pas brtson pa drag pos /
NK121(ko)004:905: zla ba yar ngo'i dpes mtshon nas goms pa gong du 'phel bar byas la bsgom /
NK121(ko)004:906: smra bsam brjod med ye shes dam pa'i spyod yul du gyur pa rgyal ba'i yum gyi dgongs don /
NK121(ko)004:907: kha chus bkang ba'i dpes mtshon nas dran snang brjod med bde ba chen por bsgom /
NK121(ko)004:908: khug sna bden med kyi dpes grags snang /
NK121(ko)004:909: ste 'jig rten chos brgyad kyi rtog pa /
NK121(ko)004:911: sems nyid du stong pa nam mkha' lta bu'i don /
NK121(ko)004:912: chu dang chu bur gyi dpes mtshon nas gnyug ma khog stong du bsgom mo bu //
NK121(ko)004:914: spyod pa nyams rtogs dang ldan par bstan pa ni /
NK121(ko)004:916: bag ma gsar bag dang ldan pa ltar ngo tsha dang khrel yod shes par bya zhing /
NK121(ko)004:917: smyon pa dran tshad byed pa lta bu'i chos dang 'gal ba'i las mi byed pa'i don te /
NK121(ko)004:918: bag ma dang smyon pa'i dpes mtshon nas 'jig rten pa dang rgyab log tu spyad /
NK121(ko)004:919: chos can gyi snang ba sna tshogs /
NK121(ko)004:920: rgya mtsho dang nya mo'i dpes mtshon nas chos nyid las mi 'da' bar spyod /
NK121(ko)004:922: nag la me mched kyi dpes mtshon nas cir snang ye shes su spyod /
NK121(ko)004:923: chos dang chos can nam snang stong dbyer med pa /
NK121(ko)004:924: lan tsh+wa chur thim pa'i dpes mtshon nas du ma ro gcig tu spyod do bu //
NK121(ko)004:926: nyams myong 'char tshul bstan pa ni /
NK121(ko)004:929: bu chung me long gi dpes mtshon nas rtog 'dzin med pa'i nyams /
NK121(ko)004:930: nyams rtogs gsar du skyes pa /
NK121(ko)004:931: dbul mos gter rnyed pa'i dpes sngar ma skyes pa'i ye shes skye ba'i nyams /
NK121(ko)004:932: thag chod kyi gdeng rnyed pa /
NK121(ko)004:933: thi bya tshang 'jug dang seng ge'i dpes mtshon nas nyams dang rtsis gdab med pa'i nyams /
NK121(ko)004:934: theg pa dman pa'i lta spyod kyis mi 'jigs pa /
NK121(ko)004:935: was seng ge mi 'jigs pa'i dpes mtshon nas grub mthas skrag sngangs med pa'i nyams so bu /
NK121(ko)004:937: nyams myong las rtags 'char ba ni /
NK121(ko)004:939: nyams rtogs nang du rgyas pa /
NK121(ko)004:940: bum nang mar me'i dpes mtshon nas rig pa kha gsal gyi rtags /
NK121(ko)004:941: 'di la shes bya gshis thog grol ba'i chos bzhi ste /
NK121(ko)004:942: rang gis rang grol ba lcags kyis lcags gcod pa lta bu /
NK121(ko)004:943: gcig thog tu gcig grol ba snang sems dbyer med
NK121(ko)004:944: mes me 'bar ba lta bu rang ngo rang gis
NK121(ko)004:945: shes pas gshis thog tu grol ba nam mkha' la
NK121(ko)004:947: snang ba rang snang du ngo shes pa ma dang bu 'phrad pa lta bu'o //
NK121(ko)004:949: rgyal po gdan la bzhugs pa'i dpes mtshon nas 'dod yon la blo mi 'jug pa'i rtags /
NK121(ko)004:950: longs med kyi blo sna mi btung ba'am chos kun skye med du thag chod pa /
NK121(ko)004:951: nad pa dur khrod kyi dpes mtshon nas skye med yid la byed pa'i rtags /
NK121(ko)004:953: phug ron dang khra yis mtshon nas nyon mongs pa thog bardzisa byed pa'i rtags so //
NK121(ko)004:955: nyams rtogs dang mi ldan na 'khor bar rang dbang med par skye bar bstan pa ni /
NK121(ko)004:956: 7 rgyal po sgyu mas bslus pa'i dpe ste /
NK121(ko)004:957: rgyal po mig yor gyi bden pa bzhi la /
NK121(ko)004:958: dngos med la dngos por bzung ba //
NK121(ko)004:959: smig rgyu chur mthong gi dpe yis mtshon nas 'dod yon 'khrul par ma shes pas 'khyams /
NK121(ko)004:960: de ma yin la der bzung ba /
NK121(ko)004:961: thag pa sbrul mthong gi dpe yis mtshon nas rang 'khrul par ma shes pas 'khyams /
NK121(ko)004:962: ma rtogs par rtogs spyod byed pa /
NK121(ko)004:963: ne tsos rma bya'i lad mo byas pas shi ba'i dpe /
NK121(ko)004:964: ne tso dug bzos kyi dpe yis mtshon nas dngos po la bden par zhen pas 'khyams /
NK121(ko)004:965: med pa la yod par bzung bas rang dbang med par chags sdang gi 'khor ba /
NK121(ko)004:966: byis pa chang stong gis zid nas 'dir zan chang
NK121(ko)004:967: yod ces mgo bskor ba'i dpes mtshon nas snang bas
NK121(ko)004:970: rgyud tshod mthon po'i dam bca'/
NK121(ko)004:972: 'di rnams mi 'byung ba'i rgyu dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas dpang du btsug pa yin pas /
NK121(ko)004:973: dam bca' nyams pa'i nyes dmigs dpag tu med cing /
NK121(ko)004:974: ma nyams na yon tan bsam gyis mi khyab ste
NK121(ko)004:975: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sras kyi
NK121(ko)004:976: thu bor gyur pas na thun tshod re'i nang du
NK121(ko)004:977: bsngo bgrang bya zhing nyams na bshags sdom drag pos
NK121(ko)004:979: de la bde sdug thams cad rang gi sngon gyi las snang du shes pas /
NK121(ko)004:980: bdag la 'jig rten gyi khams dgrar langs kyang chos nyid las ma 'khrul bar bya /
NK121(ko)004:981: 'khrul na dus gsum sangs rgyas bslus so //
NK121(ko)004:982: rtag tu dran shes kyis zin pas bdag gis ci
NK121(ko)004:983: byed kyang chos nyid skye med kyi ngang las ma
NK121(ko)004:984: 'khyal bar bya / 'khyal na dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas bslus so //
NK121(ko)004:989: tshul khrims la ngo lkog med /
NK121(ko)004:990: las 'bras la yid ches pa'i sgo nas /
NK121(ko)004:991: bdag gis lus srog la bab kyang chos rang ma shor bar bya'o //
NK121(ko)004:992: shor na dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas bslus so //
NK121(ko)004:993: khe nyan gyi khyad par dang bka' drin dran pas /
NK121(ko)004:994: bdag gi bla ma dam pa dang dam tshig rdul tsam yang ma nyams par bya /
NK121(ko)004:995: nyams na dus gsum sangs rgyas bslus so //
NK121(ko)004:996: 'chi ba rjes dran dang 'khor ba'i nyes dmigs bsam pa sogs kyis /
NK121(ko)004:997: bdag gis dus 'dir tshe 'di'i snyan grags sogs chos
NK121(ko)004:998: brgyad mi bsgrub par byang chub kyi sems sbyong ba'i
NK121(ko)004:1000: tshe 'di bsgrubs shing sems sbyong ba la brtson par ma byas na dus gsum sangs rgyas bslus so //
NK121(ko)004:1001: mdo rgyud kun nas gsungs pa bzhin /
NK121(ko)004:1002: bla ma rje btsun rnams rdo rje sems dpa' dngos su blta zhing mos gus bya /
NK121(ko)004:1003: de ltar ma byas na dus gsum sangasargyasa bslus so //
NK121(ko)004:1006: gnyis med ye shes su shes pas /
NK121(ko)004:1007: bdag gis phyi nang gi dngos po thams cad sems su shes par byas la chags sdang mi bya /
NK121(ko)004:1008: de byas na dus gsum sangs rgyas bslus so //
NK121(ko)004:1009: mar shes drin dran drin gzo'i bsam pas /
NK121(ko)004:1010: bdag gis snying rje chen po bskyed cing sems can gyi don bsgrub par bya /
NK121(ko)004:1011: gal te sems bskyed las 'das te /
NK121(ko)004:1012: rang gcig pu'i don bsgrubs na dus gsum sangs rgyas bslus so //
NK121(ko)004:1013: phyi nang gi dngos po thams cad la bden par zhen pa'i dbang gis /
NK121(ko)004:1014: gnyis 'dzin thams cad bdud kyi las yin pas gnyis med du shes par bya /
NK121(ko)004:1015: ma byas na dus gsum sangs rgyas bslus so //
NK121(ko)004:1016: bdag gi lus 'di la brten nas sangs rgyas kyi
NK121(ko)004:1017: 'bras tshol ba la spyod lam bzhir dran pas zin
NK121(ko)004:1018: par byas te lus srung ba sogs /
NK121(ko)004:1020: ma byas na dus gsum sangs rgyas bslus so bu //
NK121(ko)004:1022: ma g.yengs pa'i gdam ngag gi sgo nas bsgom pa ni /
NK121(ko)004:1024: ting nge 'dzin gyi bzhag thabs kyi gnad la mkhas pa /
NK121(ko)004:1025: dpe bas ma gtan chos drug las gsungs bzhin /
NK121(ko)004:1026: shes pa 'dzin med kyi blo las ma yengs pa mda' srong ba lta bu /
NK121(ko)004:1027: skye med kyi don la blos cir yang mi 'dzin pa /
NK121(ko)004:1028: dran med kyi dbyings las ma yengs pa gyad kyi
NK121(ko)004:1029: rtsal sbyong ba lta bu yang na rtsi sbyor ba
NK121(ko)004:1030: ste lha bzo mkhas pas tshon rtsi sbyor ba lta
NK121(ko)004:1031: bu'o // chos spyan thams cad chos nyid las ma 'das pas rang bzhin gnyis med dam /
NK121(ko)004:1032: mnyam nyid kyi klong las ma yengs pa nya 'dzin pa lta bu /
NK121(ko)004:1033: lta ba mthar 'dzin dang bsgom pa blos byas las grol bas /
NK121(ko)004:1034: bsam du med pa las ma yengs pa tsher ma 'don pa lta bu'o bu //
NK121(ko)004:1035: le'u sum cu so bdun pa /
NK121(ko)004:1036: bzhag thabs gdams ngag gi sgo nas bsgom pa ni /
NK121(ko)004:1038: spyi tshogs drug gi yul la nang de dar 'dzin gyi mkhan po stor ba /
NK121(ko)004:1039: shes pa 'dzin med had po'i gdams ngag gi mgo skam po lta bu //
NK121(ko)004:1040: 'di'i bzhag thabs kyi gdams ngag dngos ni /
NK121(ko)004:1041: dmigs med kyi klong du rtsol med du bzhag /'dus ma byas pa'i dbyings su ma bcos par bzhag /
NK121(ko)004:1042: thams cad rang sems su shar ba la nga bdag med par bzhag /
NK121(ko)004:1043: ma bcos pa'i klong du mi dmigs par bzhag /
NK121(ko)004:1044: gzung 'dzin med pa'i klong du rang lugs su bzhag /
NK121(ko)004:1045: ma skyes pa'i klong du brjod bral du bzhag pa ste drug go /
NK121(ko)004:1046: shes pa ce re long gi gdams ngag skyes bu dug zos pa lta bu /
NK121(ko)004:1047: dpe thang khrom zos pa'i mig la skra shad 'dzag pa /
NK121(ko)004:1048: don tshogs drug gi yul snang bden med du shes pas bden 'dzin log pa /
NK121(ko)004:1049: gdams ngag dngos la gdod nas ma skyes pa'i chos drug ste /
NK121(ko)004:1050: gdod nas ma chags pa'i chos nyid /
NK121(ko)004:1051: ma zhen rang grol gyi rtogs pa /
NK121(ko)004:1052: ma bzung rang byung gi shar lugs /
NK121(ko)004:1053: ma byas lhun grub nyams myong /
NK121(ko)004:1054: ma skyes bdag med kyi gnas lugs /
NK121(ko)004:1055: ma btsal rang shar gyi rol pa'o //
NK121(ko)004:1056: phyi snang ba la nang zhen 'dzin gyis ma bslad pa /
NK121(ko)004:1057: shes pa rtsis med kyi gdams ngag bu chung lta bu /
NK121(ko)004:1059: ma bcos sems kyi chos nyid /
NK121(ko)004:1060: mi rtog sems kyi lta ba /
NK121(ko)004:1061: mi dmigs sems kyi ye shes /
NK121(ko)004:1062: ma yengs sems kyi bsgom pa /
NK121(ko)004:1063: mi g.yo sems kyi ngo bo /
NK121(ko)004:1064: mi mda' sems kyi dam tshig /
NK121(ko)004:1065: mi gtong sems kyi spyod pa'o //
NK121(ko)004:1066: shes pa cog bzhag hor rdol gyi gdams ngag skyes bu'i snying bton pa lta bu'o bu /
NK121(ko)004:1067: dpe skyes bu snying bton pa sos re med cing bsam rtog rgyun chad pa /
NK121(ko)004:1068: don gdams ngag cog bzhag hor rdor te ma bcos rang lugs su cog ger bzhag pas /
NK121(ko)004:1069: 'jog mkhan dang bdag po med pa hor rdol ba
NK121(ko)004:1070: yul shes sna tshogs su shar ba la gnyer med
NK121(ko)004:1071: par 'dzin med lhug par 'jog pa ste /
NK121(ko)004:1072: bden gnyis dbyer med kyi gnas lugs la /
NK121(ko)004:1073: rgyu rkyen rtsol sgrub dang bral bar rig pa stong
NK121(ko)004:1074: gsal gyi ngang la ma bcos gnyug mar 'jog pa'o
NK121(ko)004:1076: rang babs su bzhag pa'i gdams ngag ni //
NK121(ko)004:1078: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa ye nas rang la yod pas nam yang /
NK121(ko)004:1079: stor rgyu med par ma tshol gsal la rtog pa med pa 'dug /
NK121(ko)004:1080: sems ye nas ma bzung ma bcings pas /
NK121(ko)004:1081: shor rgyu med par ma 'gugs bde la mi rtog par 'jug /
NK121(ko)004:1082: yengs yul chos nyid las ma 'das pas /
NK121(ko)004:1083: yengs pa med par ma yengs lhang nge me re zhog /
NK121(ko)004:1084: ji ltar 'jog na ma bcos pa'i chos drug ste /
NK121(ko)004:1090: rtsol na sgrib pas ma btsal /
NK121(ko)004:1095: mi rtsol bar rang lugs su 'jog pa'o //
NK121(ko)004:1096: yid la bya rgyu'i chos med cing byas pa'i chos kyis byar med mi 'grub pas /
NK121(ko)004:1097: bya rgyu med par ma brel thang nger sbreng nge /
NK121(ko)004:1098: ste nyams len thang lhod med par gzhu brdung ba'i rgyud bzhin du 'dug cig bu //
NK121(ko)004:1100: shugs 'byung 'gags pa med pa sems kyiganada ni /
NK121(ko)004:1101: 7 sems kyi gnad bzung ba drug la /
NK121(ko)004:1102: bzhi cha gsum bral gyi rig pa gzung 'dzin gyi
NK121(ko)004:1103: rtog pas ma bslad pa'i ma bcos thad ka 'di
NK121(ko)004:1104: gnyug ma'i chos sku yin pas /
NK121(ko)004:1105: dmigs pa rang yan gyi gdams ngag gis sems zin par byed pa /
NK121(ko)004:1106: las zin pa'i skyes bu'i dpes mtshon nas yid dal btsal ba sems kyi gnad /
NK121(ko)004:1107: dngos 'dzin gyi bden zhen las grol bas bzang ngan gyi rtog pa'i 'phrig med pa /
NK121(ko)004:1108: skyes bu nad kyis zin pa'i dpes mtshon nas 'phrig pa med pa sems kyi gnad /
NK121(ko)004:1109: ye nas sangs ma rgyas pa'i chos gcig kyang med
NK121(ko)004:1110: pas gang la'ang dgag sgrub kyi gza' gtad med pa
NK121(ko)004:1111: / skyon pa g.yang la 'phyong ba'i dpes mtshon nas tshom tshom med pa sems kyi gnad /
NK121(ko)004:1112: cir snang ye shes su grol bas /
NK121(ko)004:1116: 'bras bu la yid smon dang bral ba /
NK121(ko)004:1117: dpe rang nyid kyi don du gnyer ba'i mi dang
NK121(ko)004:1118: 'phrad zin pa'i dpes mtshon nas re dogs med pa
NK121(ko)004:1119: sems kyi gnad / a ti'i rang skad bton pas theg dman zil gyis gnon pa /
NK121(ko)004:1120: seng ge sder chags kyi gseb tu 'gro ba'i dpes mtshon nas nyams nga med pa sems kyi gnad /
NK121(ko)004:1121: gnas lugs rang gsal sgrib g.yog dang bral ba /
NK121(ko)004:1122: til gyi mar me'i dpes mtshon nas gsal la rtog pa med pa sems kyi gnad do bu //
NK121(ko)004:1124: lta bsgom spyod 'bras rang chad las gzhan du med par bstan pa ni /
NK121(ko)004:1125: 7 mi tshol ba'i chos bzhi la /
NK121(ko)004:1126: blo bral chos nyid kyi dgongs pa rang chus su
NK121(ko)004:1127: gnas pas blos byas phyogs 'dzin gyi lta bas gsar
NK121(ko)004:1129: nyi ma 'od tshol ba'i dpes mtshon nas gza' gtad med pa'i lta bas gtad can du mi tshol /
NK121(ko)004:1130: rang babs gnyug ma'i don la dmigs gtad sems 'dzin gyis gsar du bsgom mi dgos pa /
NK121(ko)004:1131: yid bzhin gyi nor bu dgos 'dod mi tshol ba'i
NK121(ko)004:1132: dpes dmigs gtad med pa'i bsgom pas dmigs gtad can
NK121(ko)004:1133: du mi tshol / nyon mongs ye shes sogs spang
NK121(ko)004:1134: gnyen ro mnyam pas blang dor gyi spyad bya spyod
NK121(ko)004:1136: skyes bu rang nyid skyes bu rang la mi tshol
NK121(ko)004:1137: ba'i dpes mtshon nas blang dor med pa'i spyod pas
NK121(ko)004:1138: blang dor can du mi tshol /
NK121(ko)004:1139: ye sangs rgyas pa'i 'bras bu rang la gnas pas
NK121(ko)004:1140: gzhan la rag mi las pa rgyal po gdan non
NK121(ko)004:1142: btsad po btsad po la mi ldag pa'i dpes mtshon
NK121(ko)004:1143: nas re dogs med pa'i 'bras bu re dogs can
NK121(ko)004:1145: de ltar 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad rang bzhin
NK121(ko)004:1146: dbyer med pas re dog spros rtsol las 'das pa'i
NK121(ko)004:1147: chos nyid mnyam pa'i don las ma g.yos par bya'o
NK121(ko)004:1148: // de'ang lhag pa'i sems kyi bslab pa'i le'u rnams rnam bshad du gong 'og gi 'brel bsdebs nas /
NK121(ko)004:1149: le'u sum cu pa'i rjes su so drug dang so dgu'i bar dang /
NK121(ko)004:1150: de mtshams su shes rab kyi bslab pa'i nang gi le'u bdun cu rtsa bdun pa yar drangs /
NK121(ko)004:1151: de nas le'u so gcig pa nas so lnga'i bar dang /
NK121(ko)004:1152: de'i rjes su le'u bzhi bcu pa bzhag par mdzad
NK121(ko)004:1153: na'ang 'dir ni rtsa ba rang gi dkyus bzhin du
NK121(ko)004:1155: de rnams kyi sgo nas bar do dang /
NK121(ko)004:1156: sgyu 'phrul dang mthun par lhag pa ting nge 'dzin
NK121(ko)004:1157: gyi bslab pa la brten nas lam khyer lta sgom
NK121(ko)004:1158: dang bcas pa bu chung gso ba lta bu /
NK121(ko)004:1159: thabs shes zung du 'brel ba mkha' la bya 'phur
NK121(ko)004:1160: gyi tshul du blo che chung kun la mtshams par
NK121(ko)004:1161: bshad pa'i gdams ngag thal lo //
NK121(ko)004:1162: zhal gyi gdams pa brgyad cu pa las thabs bsam
NK121(ko)004:1163: gtan rtse gcig la gdams pa'i skabs te gsum pa'o
NK121(ko)004:1164: // rtsa ba'i sa bcad bzhi pa /
NK121(ko)004:1165: ngo bo rnam par dag pa lhag pa shes rab
NK121(ko)004:1166: kyi bslab pa la gdams pa le'u sum cu rtsa
NK121(ko)004:1169: yin pa bcu gnyis kyi lta ba bstan pa ni /
NK121(ko)004:1170: 7 smad sems phyogs kyi dgongs pa spu gri so brteb lta bu /
NK121(ko)004:1171: don 'khor gsum mi dmigs pa'i shes rab kyis nyon
NK121(ko)004:1172: mongs rnam rtog thams cad du rtsa bral du gcod
NK121(ko)004:1173: pa ste / gcod lugs 'khor 'das sogs gzhi lam
NK121(ko)004:1174: 'bras bu'i chos thams cad rang sems skye med kyi
NK121(ko)004:1175: rol bar shar bar bzang ngan med par mtha' grol
NK121(ko)004:1179: mtshan nyid gnyis med sogs su ngo sprod pa ni /
NK121(ko)004:1181: chos kun rtsa ba sems su 'dus pa'i phyir //
NK121(ko)004:1182: des na rtsa ba'i don de bstan par bya //
NK121(ko)004:1186: rang sems chos nyid skye med kyi don de gar
NK121(ko)004:1187: yang ma spas kyang mtshan ma'i spyod yul du sus
NK121(ko)004:1188: kyang / mthong ba med pa yin /
NK121(ko)004:1189: ye nas rang chas su ma bral bar yod kyang sngar rang gis rang ngo ma shes pa yin /
NK121(ko)004:1190: ci yi ngo bor yang ma grub pas brtags na
NK121(ko)004:1191: mi mthong yang ma brtags nyams dga' tsam du 'khor
NK121(ko)004:1192: 'das kyi chos kun ma 'gags par cir yang snang
NK121(ko)004:1193: ba yin / don la med bzhin 'khrul snang sna
NK121(ko)004:1194: tshogs snang yang rang gi rang bzhin cir yang ma
NK121(ko)004:1195: grub pas dngos po med pa yin /
NK121(ko)004:1196: rgyun ring bskal par srid par 'khyams kyang bde gshegs
NK121(ko)004:1197: snying po'i rang bzhin la stor 'bral med pa yin
NK121(ko)004:1198: / 'khor 'das sna tshogs su snang yang chos nyid
NK121(ko)004:1199: kyi rang bzhin la nam yang 'gyur ba med pa
NK121(ko)004:1200: / yin / dngos por grub pa rdul phra rab
NK121(ko)004:1201: kyi cha tsam med par nam mkha' bzhin du kun
NK121(ko)004:1203: nam mkha' lta bu'i stong pa nyid de'i ngang la
NK121(ko)004:1204: rgyu 'bras rten 'byung gi chos sna tshogs ma 'gags
NK121(ko)004:1206: sems rta rmu rgod dang 'dra bas sgrims te tsab tsum mang na mi zin glod na zin pas /
NK121(ko)004:1207: ma bzung ma btags gar yang chags pa'am gnas pa yin /
NK121(ko)004:1208: zhi lhag zung du 'brel bas khyung mkha' la lding ba bzhin /
NK121(ko)004:1209: 'degs pa med par chos nyid kyi mkha' la 'gro ba yin /
NK121(ko)004:1210: chos nyid ci yang ma yin pa las cir yang 'char du rung bas /
NK121(ko)004:1211: rtsol ba med par ci sgrub 'grub pa yin /
NK121(ko)004:1212: sems nyid la kha dog dbyibs gzugs dang mtshan ma
NK121(ko)004:1213: med par ci ltar ltas shing bsgom pa de lta
NK121(ko)004:1214: bu snang ba yin no bu /
NK121(ko)004:1215: mdor na rang bzhin skye med du 'dug pas dngos gzhi med /
NK121(ko)004:1216: rol pa 'gag med du 'dug pas sna tshogs su shar /
NK121(ko)004:1217: chos nyid gnyis med du 'dug pas bden zhen bya rgyu med /
NK121(ko)004:1218: blo ngo bo nyid du grol bas chos nyid las 'da' sa med par ngo sprad pa'o //
NK121(ko)004:1220: yid ches bcu gnyis kyis blo la dam bca' ba ni /
NK121(ko)004:1221: don rjen par mthong bas blo la the tshom med par yid ches bcu gnyis la /
NK121(ko)004:1222: snang srid thams cad nam mkhar skye 'jig byed pa'i
NK121(ko)004:1223: dpes don 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad de bzhin
NK121(ko)004:1224: nyid du gcig pas rang bzhin med par yid ches
NK121(ko)004:1225: / chos kun gyi rtsa ba sems su 'dus pas
NK121(ko)004:1226: sangs rgyas gzhan nas btsal du med par yid ches
NK121(ko)004:1227: / / sems la rang bzhin gyis skye ba dang
NK121(ko)004:1228: 'gag pa med pas 'dus byas min par yid ches
NK121(ko)004:1229: / / / snang ba thams cad 'khrul pa yin
NK121(ko)004:1230: pas don la dgra gnyen gnyis su med par ngo
NK121(ko)004:1232: 'khrul pa'i bya ba byas tshad duhkha ste sdug bsngal
NK121(ko)004:1233: gyi rgyu yin pas chos nyid kyi don la bya
NK121(ko)004:1235: chos dbyings skye med ni chos kun gyi rang bzhin
NK121(ko)004:1236: yin pas rang bzhin gnyis su med par yid ches
NK121(ko)004:1237: / rang sems skye med kyi don /
NK121(ko)004:1238: rtogs na sangs rgyas yin pas lam la bgrod du med par yid ches /
NK121(ko)004:1239: cir snang mi bden sgyu ma lta bu yin pas
NK121(ko)004:1240: chags sdang gis yid dkrug tu med par yid ches
NK121(ko)004:1241: / snang sems du ma ra gcig pas chags sdang
NK121(ko)004:1242: sogs dug lnga'i rtog pa rang bzhin skye med yin
NK121(ko)004:1243: / par yid ches / nyon mongs skye yul dgra
NK121(ko)004:1244: gnyen sogs blos gsar du btags pa tsam las rang
NK121(ko)004:1245: gi ngo bos grub pa med pas thams cad sems
NK121(ko)004:1247: 'khor 'das kyi chos kun gyi 'byung gnas yin pas sems nyid dbyings kyi yum yin par yid ches /
NK121(ko)004:1248: nam mkha' bzhin du chos kun gyi gnas yin pas
NK121(ko)004:1249: sems kyi chos nyid gnas lugs yangs pa chen por
NK121(ko)004:1252: chos nyid dgu ldan du mthong ba'i gdams ngag ni /
NK121(ko)004:1256: chos thams cad rang bzhin stong par mthong /
NK121(ko)004:1257: chos kun gyi rtsa ba sems su mthong /
NK121(ko)004:1258: rang sems kyi ngo bo skye med du mthong /
NK121(ko)004:1259: snang ba bcu bdun sogs 'char tshul ma 'gags pas /
NK121(ko)004:1260: gnas skabs nges med du mthong /
NK121(ko)004:1261: chos thams cad kyi chos nyid bden med du mthong /
NK121(ko)004:1262: sna tshogs su snang yang chos nyid dbyings kyi yin lugs 'gyur med du mthong /
NK121(ko)004:1263: rang byung rkyen dang bral bas /
NK121(ko)004:1264: gnas lugs gnyis med du mthong /
NK121(ko)004:1265: rkyen gyis sna tshogs su snang bas gzhi phyogs med du mthong /
NK121(ko)004:1267: gshis spros bral du mthong ngo bu //
NK121(ko)004:1269: dam pa bdun ldan du mthong ba ni /
NK121(ko)004:1270: sgom mkhan rang gi blo la bdag po dang gnyer med pas grol ba /
NK121(ko)004:1272: yod med snang stong sogs dmigs gtad kyi mis 'tshol bar /
NK121(ko)004:1273: yid bzhag pa dang bral ba ni bzhag pa dam pa'o //
NK121(ko)004:1274: dmigs su med pa'i chos nyid la gzung 'dzin gyi
NK121(ko)004:1275: blo'i dmigs pa dang bral ba ni dmigs pa dam
NK121(ko)004:1276: pa'o // rtog mi rtog gnyis ka blo las ma
NK121(ko)004:1277: 'das shing blos byas kyis blo bral gyi don la
NK121(ko)004:1278: pa'o // bsgribs pas / mi rtog pa nyid mi bsgom pa ni mi rtog pa dam pa'o //
NK121(ko)004:1279: shes bya gang la'ang rten mi 'cha' ba ni rten dam pa'o //
NK121(ko)004:1280: yul du byas te snang stong sogs cir yang mi bsgom pa ni bsgom pa dam pa'o //
NK121(ko)004:1281: ched du sems sems byung gi 'gyu ba ma bkag
NK121(ko)004:1282: la yengs pa med pa ni bsam gtan dam pa'o
NK121(ko)004:1283: // sems tshogs brgyad kyi yul gang la'ang mi 'jug pa ni ting nge 'dzin dam pa'o bu /
NK121(ko)004:1284: mdor na 'di thams cad dmigs gtad dang bcos bslad med par 'jog pa yin no //
NK121(ko)004:1286: dbang po drug gi sgo nas tha dad ma spangs gnyis med du mthong ba'i gdams ngag ni //
NK121(ko)004:1287: chos nyid la don la nges shes skyes pa /
NK121(ko)004:1288: shes rab kyi dbang po drug la /
NK121(ko)004:1289: gzugs snang skye med du shes pas der 'dzin dang bral bas /
NK121(ko)004:1290: rang snang gi gzugs mthong ba shes rab kyi spyan /
NK121(ko)004:1291: chos nyid stong pa nyid kyi don go ba shes rab kyi snyan /
NK121(ko)004:1292: rang bzhin skye med du tshor ba shes rab kyi shangs /
NK121(ko)004:1293: sna tshogs gnyis med du myong ba shes rab kyi ljags /
NK121(ko)004:1295: chos nyid la reg pa shes rab kyi lus /
NK121(ko)004:1296: rang snang du shar ba thams cad skye med rang
NK121(ko)004:1297: du shar ba yin par shes pa shes rab kyi
NK121(ko)004:1298: yid do bu // le'u zhe drug pa /
NK121(ko)004:1299: mthong lugs de nyid kyis tha dad du ma spangs gnyis med du mthong ba ni /
NK121(ko)004:1300: rang sems chos nyid du grol na phyi rol gyi snang ba thams cad chos nyid du 'char bas /
NK121(ko)004:1301: shes rab kyi yul drug la /
NK121(ko)004:1302: chos nyid gsal stong du mthong ba shes rab kyi gzugs /
NK121(ko)004:1303: bdag po med pa sgra snyan bzhin du /
NK121(ko)004:1304: rang shar du go ba shes rab kyi sgra /
NK121(ko)004:1305: bla ma'i gdams ngag gis tshim pa shes rab kyi dri /
NK121(ko)004:1306: chos thams cad kyi don skye med du nyams su myong ba shes rab kyi ro //
NK121(ko)004:1307: chos nyid bde ba chen po la reg pa shes rab kyi reg bya /
NK121(ko)004:1308: gnas lugs chos nyid kyi rang ngo rang gis shes pa shes rab kyi chos so bu //
NK121(ko)004:1310: brtags na med pa'i sgo nas med pa drug ldan du mthong ba ni /
NK121(ko)004:1312: chos thams cad ci'i ngo bor yang bden par grub pa med pas /
NK121(ko)004:1313: cir yang ma mthong ba ni mthong ba yang dag pa'o //
NK121(ko)004:1314: chos nyid kyi don la thos bya thos byed gnyis med pas /
NK121(ko)004:1315: cir yang thos pa med pa ni thos pa yang dag pa'o //
NK121(ko)004:1316: don la tshor bya tshor byed gnyis med pas /
NK121(ko)004:1317: cir yang tshor ba med pa ni tshor ba yang dag pa'o //
NK121(ko)004:1318: de bzhin du cir yang ma myong ba dam pa'o //
NK121(ko)004:1319: bden rdzun sogs yul gang la yang blos ma reg pa ni reg pa yang dag pa'o //
NK121(ko)004:1320: chos thams cad kyi mtshan nyid /
NK121(ko)004:1321: cir yang rig pa med pa ni rig pa dam pa'o //
NK121(ko)004:1323: rtsol med drug gi chos nyid la blang dor mi byed par bstan pa ni //
NK121(ko)004:1324: chos thams cad bya rtsol dang bral bar 'jog shes na gshis yin lugs su grol bas /
NK121(ko)004:1325: rtsol ba med pa'i dgongs pa drug la /
NK121(ko)004:1326: rang sems skye med kyi nam mkha' la blta bya
NK121(ko)004:1327: lta byed gnyis med pas bcos bsgyur dgag sgrub dang
NK121(ko)004:1328: bral ba'i lta ba rang sor bzhag pas blo la
NK121(ko)004:1329: yang dog med par cam cam gyis gnas pa'o //
NK121(ko)004:1331: 'dzin med la phyi nang gi rtog pa'i gra zur med pas chos nyid zhi mal mal /
NK121(ko)004:1332: ma bcos shugs 'byung gi spyod pa la dang du
NK121(ko)004:1333: len pa dang dor bya'i 'bad rtsol med pa ci
NK121(ko)004:1334: dga' dga'/ yin lugs mngon du gyur pas 'bras bu
NK121(ko)004:1335: la thob ma thob kyi re dogs med pa zhi
NK121(ko)004:1336: dga' dga'/ thes thes te / gzung 'dzin gyi rnam rtog rang sar grol ba'o //
NK121(ko)004:1337: chos can gyi dngos po gang la'ang bzang ngan med par chos nyid kyi ngang du mnyam phril phril /
NK121(ko)004:1338: 'khor ba ma spangs ye nas myang 'das su grol
NK121(ko)004:1339: bas sems la zug rngu med pa bde lhan lhan
NK121(ko)004:1340: no bu // le'u zhe dgu pa /
NK121(ko)004:1341: brda' chos bcu drug gi gdams ngag bstan pa ni /
NK121(ko)004:1343: mtshan ma'i sgrib g.yog dang bral ba'i rig pa rtag tu gter bur byung /
NK121(ko)004:1344: dngos 'dzin dang bden zhen gyi gnyen por stong nyid kyi khrus chen rtag tu gyis /
NK121(ko)004:1345: stong nyid dang snying rje'i nyi zla lag pas zungs /
NK121(ko)004:1346: lta sgom gyi 'khor lo klad la bskor /
NK121(ko)004:1347: rang sems 'phrul gyi me long la ltos /
NK121(ko)004:1348: nyon mongs pa'i dug nad sos par gyis /
NK121(ko)004:1349: dug gsum mam gsung 'dzin gyi thag pas bcing pa khrol /
NK121(ko)004:1350: sdig pa'i grogs po gcan dang 'dra ba'i gzeb nas grol /
NK121(ko)004:1351: rang byung gi ye shes ngos zin pa byas nas rig pa stong gsal shel gyi bum par sdong /
NK121(ko)004:1352: dad brtson dran shes bag yod kyis chos spyod bcu
NK121(ko)004:1353: sogs kyi spyod pa rin chen skas la mal nas
NK121(ko)004:1354: yar 'dzogs / bdag 'dzin gyi ljon shing rtsad nas chod /
NK121(ko)004:1355: rig pa mu dang bral ba nam mkha' mthongs su nyol /
NK121(ko)004:1356: rang gi 'gyu byed kyi rtog pa rang srog rang gis chod /
NK121(ko)004:1357: cir snang chos nyid du shar ba'i gser gling du rgyugs /
NK121(ko)004:1358: chags sdang gi tshad pa la ting nge 'dzin gyi bsil sman lus la chongs /
NK121(ko)004:1359: chos thams cad ming tsam las don la ma grub pa /
NK121(ko)004:1360: nam mkha'i me tog thus shig bu //
NK121(ko)004:1362: blang dor med par dgag sgrub dang bral ba'i lta ba ni /
NK121(ko)004:1364: rnam rtog gang shar chos nyid skye med pas rtog pa la zhe ma sdang /
