NK121(ko)004:1365: mi rtog ye shes logs su bsgom du med /
NK121(ko)004:1366: nyon mongs rtog tshogs spangs pa'i pha rol na ye shes sam chos nyid la 'dod ma chags /
NK121(ko)004:1367: chags na 'khor bar 'khyams pa'i rgyu byed /
NK121(ko)004:1368: chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid du shes pas rang gi ting nge 'dzin la nga ma rgyal /
NK121(ko)004:1369: mi 'dod pa dang phyin ci log gi rtog pa thams cad rang sems kyi cho 'phrul yin pas /
NK121(ko)004:1370: phyin ci log la phrag ma dog /
NK121(ko)004:1371: rang byung gi ye shes rang la yod pas /
NK121(ko)004:1372: ye shes la gti ma mug cig ste de'i don shes pas gyis shig bu //
NK121(ko)004:1374: gnas lugs kyi don la zhe gdeng bcu dang ldan par bstan pa ni /
NK121(ko)004:1375: 7 bde sdug sogs mtshan ma thams cad dbyings kyi
NK121(ko)004:1376: ngo bor grol bas gang gis kyang phan gnod med
NK121(ko)004:1378: rang byung gi ye shes sam byang chub kyi sems
NK121(ko)004:1379: la rgyu rkyen med pas dus gsum du 'pho 'gyur
NK121(ko)004:1380: dang bral ba / srid pa char ltar babs mod
NK121(ko)004:1381: byang chub kyi sems kun byed rgyal po la des
NK121(ko)004:1384: khams gsum du chu ltar 'brub mod /
NK121(ko)004:1386: rgyud drug me ltar 'bar yang mi 'tshig /
NK121(ko)004:1387: stong gsum rlung ltar g.yos mod /
NK121(ko)004:1391: stong gsum nyi mas gang mod ye shes la gsal rgyu med /
NK121(ko)004:1392: gling bar mun par chud mod ma rig pas gnag rgyu med /
NK121(ko)004:1393: skye shi ris su chad mod 'chi rgyu med /
NK121(ko)004:1394: las dbang bag chags 'dug mod ye nas gos ma myong bas gsar du spang rgyu med /
NK121(ko)004:1395: snang srid kha sbubs byas mod 'jig 'bral med do //
NK121(ko)004:1396: zhes pa ste gang gis kyang mi bardziba'i dgongs pa gdengs su gyur pa'i rdo rje'i tshig go /
NK121(ko)004:1398: dpe don 'brel ba'i sgo nas chos nyid kyi rtsis bzung ba'i gdams ngag ni /
NK121(ko)004:1400: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku ji ltar bltas kyang mdzes pa'i dpes mtshon nas /
NK121(ko)004:1401: don rtogs pa skye med kyis rtsis zin na chags
NK121(ko)004:1402: sdang gi rang rgyud pa med pas rtogs ldan gyi
NK121(ko)004:1403: spyod pa gang ltar spyod kyang bde /
NK121(ko)004:1404: ji ltar gnag pa dang 'dzum pa gnyis bzhin gcig
NK121(ko)004:1405: las mi 'da' ba'i dpes mtshon nas don 'khor 'das
NK121(ko)004:1406: kyi rnam sprul cir snang cir srid chos nyid skye
NK121(ko)004:1407: med las mi 'da'/ long ba la 'dzub mo bstan
NK121(ko)004:1408: pa dang bstan pa khyad med pa'i dpes mtshon nas
NK121(ko)004:1409: don skye med kyi dbyings las 'gag med du shar
NK121(ko)004:1410: ba'i chos kun dbyer med ro mnyam pas chos nyid
NK121(ko)004:1412: chu shing gi sdong po la snying po med pa'i
NK121(ko)004:1413: dpes mtshon nas don gcig tu bral sogs kyi gtan
NK121(ko)004:1414: tshigs gis brtags na mi rnyed pas snang srid la
NK121(ko)004:1417: mtha' bzhi rang grol gyi sgo nas ma spangs par rang snang du bstan pa'i gdams ngag ni /
NK121(ko)004:1420: 'khor 'das kyi chos kun la don skye ba med pas yod pa'i chos las grol /
NK121(ko)004:1421: rgyu rkyen rten 'brel tshogs pa'i snang cha /
NK121(ko)004:1422: kun rdzob bkag pa med pas med pa'i chos las grol /
NK121(ko)004:1423: don dam par bden gnyis sam snang stong /
NK121(ko)004:1424: tha dad kyi chos ma grub ste dbye gzhi zad
NK121(ko)004:1425: pa'i dbyer med dam gnyis med yin pas gnyis yin
NK121(ko)004:1426: las grol / blos ji ltar gzung ba bzhin /
NK121(ko)004:1427: gnyis med gnyis su 'char bas gnyis med las grol lo bu /
NK121(ko)004:1428: de la bden gnyis gcig par 'dod na /
NK121(ko)004:1429: so skye 'du byed mthong bas don dam mthong bar thal /
NK121(ko)004:1430: don dam nyon mongs skye ba'i dmigs rkyen du thal /
NK121(ko)004:1431: don dam kun rdzob dbye ba med par thal /
NK121(ko)004:1432: don dam thos bsam la mi ltos par thal ba'i skyon bzhi dang tha dad na /
NK121(ko)004:1433: don dam rtogs pa'i blos kun rdzob kyi bden zhen mi sel ba dang /
NK121(ko)004:1434: de'i chos nyid ma yin pa dang /
NK121(ko)004:1435: kun rdzob rang bzhin med pa tsam don dam ma yin pa dang /
NK121(ko)004:1436: de dag so so gzigs pa'i 'phags pa rnams la
NK121(ko)004:1437: bcing grol dus gcig du thal ba'i skyon bzhi yod
NK121(ko)004:1438: do // rang lugs la skyon de rnams med de
NK121(ko)004:1439: gcig tha dad gang du'ang mi 'dod pa'i phyir na'o
NK121(ko)004:1440: do // / yang rang gi blo gcig 'khrul ma 'khrul gyi dbang gi bden gnyis su 'jog tshe /
NK121(ko)004:1441: 'khrul dus kun rdzob 'khrul pa'i blo la don dam mi snang /
NK121(ko)004:1442: ma 'khrul don dam rtogs pa'i blo la kun rdzob
NK121(ko)004:1443: 'khrul pa mi snang bas snang min bzhin du gsungs
NK121(ko)004:1444: te / snga ma ni ngo bo gcig la ldog pa tha dad dang /
NK121(ko)004:1445: phyi ma ni gcig pa bkag pa'i tha dad de gnyis ka rnam bshad du gsungs so //
NK121(ko)004:1447: mthar thug bzhi ldan gyi sgo nas lam chos nyid du thag chod par bstan pa ni /
NK121(ko)004:1449: dpe rmi lam gyi snang ba bzhin du don /
NK121(ko)004:1450: phyi nang gi chos thams cad rang sems su shes
NK121(ko)004:1451: nas sems stong gzugs med par shes pa lta ba
NK121(ko)004:1452: mthar thug dpe sgyu ma'i skyes bu ltar don dbang
NK121(ko)004:1453: po'i sgo snga ma bkag la gzung 'dzin dang bral
NK121(ko)004:1455: dpe sprul pa'i skyes bus tshogs gnyis gsog pa bzhin /
NK121(ko)004:1456: lta spyod zung du spyod shes pa spyod pa'i mthar thug /
NK121(ko)004:1457: dpe sgyu ma'i skyes bus rmi lam gyi nor la spyod pa bzhin /
NK121(ko)004:1458: snang srid la bden 'dzin med pa nyams rtogs kyi mthar thug yin no //
NK121(ko)004:1460: brda don gyis mtshon pa'i sems kyi chos sku lnga'i gdams ngag ni /
NK121(ko)004:1461: 7 stong gsal 'gags med kun khyab kyi ye shes sam chos nyid de /
NK121(ko)004:1462: sems kyi chos sku lnga la /
NK121(ko)004:1463: rgya mtsho'i gting gi dpes mtshon nas chos nyid rig
NK121(ko)004:1464: stong rjen pa las nam yang g.yo ba med pa
NK121(ko)004:1465: chos kyi sku / ri rab kyi dpes mtshon nas
NK121(ko)004:1466: don chos nyid la 'pho 'gyur med pa chos kyi
NK121(ko)004:1467: chos kyi sku / sku / chu bo'i dpes mtshon
NK121(ko)004:1468: nas 'od gsal lam chos nyid la rgyun chad med
NK121(ko)004:1470: chu bo'i dpes mtshon nas 'od gsal chos nyid la rgyun chad med pa chos kyi sku /
NK121(ko)004:1471: nyi ma'i dpes mtshon nas ye shes gsal 'grib med pa chos kyi sku /
NK121(ko)004:1472: chu zla'i dpes mtshon nas rig pa la rtog pa med pa chos kyi sku yin no bu //
NK121(ko)004:1474: gsang sngags brda' don gyis mtshon pa'i gdams ngag ni /
NK121(ko)004:1475: 7 sems kyi ye shes drug la /
NK121(ko)004:1476: rtogs dpyod kyis ma bslad pa'i rang ngo so ma
NK121(ko)004:1477: gsung gzung 'dzin gnyis med thugs phrad kyi ye shes
NK121(ko)004:1478: / shes pa yul la ma spros ma bsdus snang sems du ma ro gcig gi ye shes /
NK121(ko)004:1479: 'khor 'das kyi chos gang la'ang ma blang ma dor re dogs med pa'i ye shes /
NK121(ko)004:1480: chos spyan sna tshogs pa'i snang ba la chos nyid
NK121(ko)004:1481: skye med kyi rgyas thebs pa rang byung gi ye
NK121(ko)004:1483: snang stong rig stong zung du 'jug pa'i ye shes /
NK121(ko)004:1484: tshogs brgyad yul dang bcas pa gdod nas stong pas /
NK121(ko)004:1485: phyi stong nang stong stong pa'i ye shes so bu //
NK121(ko)004:1488: sems kyi ngo sprod bdun la /
NK121(ko)004:1490: rang bzhin gcig tu ma nges pas /
NK121(ko)004:1491: gang ltar bltas bltas pa de ltar snang /
NK121(ko)004:1492: zhes rang sems kyi dbang gis yul gcig la'ang sna
NK121(ko)004:1493: tshogs su snang ba'i phyir phyi don rang bzhin gyis
NK121(ko)004:1494: grub pa med pas yul sems su ngo sprad /
NK121(ko)004:1495: rang sems kyi 'char cha sna tshogs gzugs brnyan bzhin
NK121(ko)004:1496: ma 'gags par shar yang rang bzhin stong nyid las
NK121(ko)004:1497: ma 'das pas / sems gzugs brnyan du ngo sprod /
NK121(ko)004:1498: rang byung ye shes kyi snang ba phyogs med du shar bas snang ba mtha' yas su ngo sprod /
NK121(ko)004:1499: nam mkha' sum phrug gi man ngag gis shes pa rten med du ngo sprod /
NK121(ko)004:1500: rang sems chos nyid du rtogs pas /
NK121(ko)004:1501: rig pa yul med du ngo sprod /
NK121(ko)004:1502: tshogs brgyad kyi yul snang don la yong ma myong bas /
NK121(ko)004:1504: don skye med la spros pa'i mtshan ma med pas /
NK121(ko)004:1505: skye med spros bral du ngo sprod do bu //
NK121(ko)004:1507: snang shar chos nyid du ngo sprod la rgyas gdab pa ni /
NK121(ko)004:1508: thams cad chos nyid du gcig pas spang blang med
NK121(ko)004:1509: pa'i don snang shar chos nyid du ngo sprod pa
NK121(ko)004:1510: drug la / rang sems chos nyid rtsal las /
NK121(ko)004:1512: mu stegs kyi rtag chad gnyis /
NK121(ko)004:1513: theg pa rim dgu'i 'dod tshul te snang ba bcu
NK121(ko)004:1514: bdun nges med du shar bas gang la'ang bden 'dzin
NK121(ko)004:1515: gyis yin pa yid gces spras su mi bzung /
NK121(ko)004:1516: thams cad chos nyid kyi rol pa yin pas bzang ngan du rtog pas min pa blos mi 'phang /
NK121(ko)004:1517: chos thams cad rgya chad phyogs lhung med pas blos gsar du gnyis med du mi bsdum /
NK121(ko)004:1519: rtog dpyod kyi blos yin min sogs gang la yang mi bsam /
NK121(ko)004:1520: chos nyid gting gsal gyi don las ma yengs pa'o bu //
NK121(ko)004:1522: snang shar chos su ngo sprod pa ni /

NK121(ko)004:1673: skye ba med pa'i klong du grol /

NK121(ko)004:1859: khyab pa la dbang 'byor bar 'gyur ro //
NK121(ko)004:1860: de yang lhag pa'i shes rab kyi bslab pa'i le'u
NK121(ko)004:1861: 'di rnams rnam bshad du gong 'og 'khrugs bsdebs nas
NK121(ko)004:1862: / le'u zhe gnyis pa'i rjes su zhe brgyad pa yar drangs /
NK121(ko)004:1863: de nas lnga bcu nas nga bzhi'i bar sbyar /
NK121(ko)004:1864: de'i rjes su drug cu re gsum dang re dgu /
NK121(ko)004:1865: de nas zhe gsum nas zhe bdun pa'i bar /
NK121(ko)004:1866: de'i rjes su drug cu re brgyad dang /
NK121(ko)004:1870: de nas nga lnga nas nga dgu'i bar /
NK121(ko)004:1871: de nas drug cu re gsum gong du song ba'i 'phros /
NK121(ko)004:1872: drug cu nas re bdun pa'i bar dang /
NK121(ko)004:1873: de nas bdun cu rtsa bdun pa sems kyi bslab pa'i skabs su song ba'i 'phros /
NK121(ko)004:1875: bdun cu rtsa dgu'i bar sbyar te bshad par mdzad na'ang /
NK121(ko)004:1876: 'dir ni rtsa ba rang gi dkyus bzhin du bris pa'o //
NK121(ko)004:1877: mdor na de rnams kyi sgo nas sems smad rdzogs
NK121(ko)004:1878: pa chen po sems phyogs kyi dgongs pa blangs nas
NK121(ko)004:1879: shan 'byed la blo dang bcas nges pa'i don dang
NK121(ko)004:1880: ldan pa spu gri so bsdebs pas pha rol gyi
NK121(ko)004:1882: 'khor ba'i rtsa ba skye med du gcod pa'i lam /
NK121(ko)004:1883: shes rab can la mtshams par bshad pa'i skabs kyi gdams ngag thal lo //
NK121(ko)004:1884: zhal gyi gdams pa brgyad cu pa las /
NK121(ko)004:1885: ngo bo shes rab dri ma med pa la gdams pa'i skabs te bzhi pa'o //
NK121(ko)004:1886: spyi don lnga pa mjug gi don /
NK121(ko)004:1888: snod brtag cing nyams su len par gdams ngag 'jug bsdu ba ni //
NK121(ko)004:1890: gdams ngag mi sbyin pa'i gnas snod kyi skyon /
NK121(ko)004:1891: 'di lta bu'i gdams ngag zab mos rgyud dgrol bar bya rgyu'i slob ma'i skyon shes nas /
NK121(ko)004:1892: ngang tshul ngan zhing byas pa mi gzo ba sogs /
NK121(ko)004:1893: snod ngan mi gzhi mi legs pa /
NK121(ko)004:1894: blo 'gyur ldog can mi brtan pa /
NK121(ko)004:1895: rang gi bla ma dang chos dang gang zag la skyon 'dogs pa /
NK121(ko)004:1896: gdams ngag zab mo thob nas rang gis /
NK121(ko)004:1897: nyams su mi len pa rnams la mi sbyin byin
NK121(ko)004:1898: kyang de la phan mi thog cing gsang ba 'chal
NK121(ko)004:1899: bas sgro skur dang bka' chad 'byung ngo //
NK121(ko)004:1900: gang la bstan pa'i yul snod ldan ni /
NK121(ko)004:1901: byas pa shes shing drin du gzo ba sogs ngang tshul bzang ba /
NK121(ko)004:1902: dad pa sogs 'gyur ldog med pas rgyud brtan pa /
NK121(ko)004:1903: chos dang gang zag sogs la dag snang che ba /
NK121(ko)004:1904: thos don sgrub pas nyams len la brtson pa rnams la sbyin /
NK121(ko)004:1905: de rnams la sbyin pas chos brgyad zin cing bstan pa la phan /
NK121(ko)004:1906: rang gzhan mang po'i don 'byung ngo //
NK121(ko)004:1907: de ltar byin nas nyams su len pa'i tshul /
NK121(ko)004:1908: snod ldan gyi slob ma des kyang bla ma sangs rgyas su blta /
NK121(ko)004:1911: gsang zhing sgrub nus na dngos grub rnam gnyis 'bad med du 'byung /
NK121(ko)004:1912: 'du 'dzi'i dben pa'i dgon pa grogs ltar bsten nas nyams su blang ngo //
NK121(ko)004:1913: des nyams myong rtogs tshad rgyas pas gangs kyi seng phrug tu 'gyur ro bu //
NK121(ko)004:1914: des snod kyi khyad par dang /
NK121(ko)004:1915: rang gi shes rgyud la yon tan ma skyes pa
NK121(ko)004:1916: skyes par byed pa gdams ngag rjes su bstan pa
NK121(ko)004:1917: thal lo // zhal gyi gdams pa brgyad cu pa
NK121(ko)004:1918: las snod dang rjes su bstan pa la gdams pa'i
NK121(ko)004:1921: rje lta dgongs kyi rtse mo bde gshegs rgya bo'i thugs bcud /
NK121(ko)004:1922: sde snod gsum gyi khog phub /
NK121(ko)004:1923: mdo sgyu sems gsum gyi gzhung bsrangs te /
NK121(ko)004:1924: dad brtson shes rab can rtse gcig gis grol pa'i gdams ngag /
NK121(ko)004:1925: rje'i zhal nas ji ltar gsung rim bzhin /
NK121(ko)004:1926: khyung po g.ya' dmar bas yi ger bkod pa'i zab
NK121(ko)004:1927: chos snying po'i snying po mthar thug pa rdzogs so
NK121(ko)004:1929: gang mtshan thos dang dran pas kyang //
NK121(ko)004:1930: rnam grol 'bras bu sbyin mdzad pa //
NK121(ko)004:1931: he ru ka dpal zur chung pa'i //
NK121(ko)004:1932: zhal gyi gdams pa brgyad cu zhes //
NK121(ko)004:1933: snga 'gyur brgyud pa'i khyad nor mchog /
NK121(ko)004:1934: rgyud lung man ngag zab mo'i gter //
NK121(ko)004:1936: deng dus 'bad med bdag gis rnyed //
NK121(ko)004:1937: de slad dga' dang spro shugs kyis //
NK121(ko)004:1938: mchan 'di bris la nyes pa'i cha //
NK121(ko)004:1939: gang mchis bla ma lha la bshags //
NK121(ko)004:1940: dge bas byang chen myur thob shog /
NK121(ko)004:1941: skye kun dpal ldan zur pa yi //
NK121(ko)004:1942: rang lugs mchog dang mi 'bral zhing //
NK121(ko)004:1943: tshul bzhin 'dzin skyong spel gsum gyis //
NK121(ko)004:1944: rang gzhan don gnyis 'byor gyur cig /
NK121(ko)004:1945: ces 7rdo rje 'chang mkhyen brtse'i dbang po'i zhal snga
NK121(ko)004:1946: nas rtsal ba'i sa gzhung spel ma nyid gzhir bzhag
NK121(ko)004:1947: thog rang 'dra'i blo dman rnams la sman pa'i bsam
NK121(ko)004:1948: pas gsal byed kyi mchan bu nyung ngu 'di yang
NK121(ko)004:1949: 'brel bshad rin po che gsal ba'i sgron me dang
NK121(ko)004:1950: bstun nas / ku s+aa li 'jam dbyangs blo gros rgya mtsho'i sgra dbyangs kyis /
NK121(ko)004:1951: shing byi smin drug zla ba'i dus tshes dge bar
NK121(ko)004:1952: bde mchog bkra shis dge 'phel du bris pa ste
NK121(ko)004:1953: / 'dis kyang nges gsang snying po'i bstan mchog yun ring du gnas pa'i rgyur gyur cig //
